\ip Israelian adarazi azenir bar av…®ribar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim garuava, nguazir God me bagha inabagha me dan…®ngamim bagha m…®zua iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n God nguazir kam…®n aven mangasa men amamangat…®. Dughiar kam…®n Josua Moses…®n danganim inigha Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n oto. Josuan ak…®nafarim, Israelian eghaghanir me nguazir kam iniasa Jordan…®n Fanem ab…®ghizir dughiam…®n ikegha ghua Kenania ko m…®soghezir dughiam…®n tu. M…®dorozir eghaghanir av…®riba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti. M…®dorozir kaba, Moses Ua God…®n Araziba Osirizir Ak…®nafarim, Sapta 20 m…®kemezir tuavimra da otifi. God a uab…® men afeziam egha a uab…® m…®dorozibar faragha ghua men inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®rizir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gamiz…® a guizbang…®ram oto.
\ip Josuan ak…®nafarim, akuar 3pla iti.
\ip 1. Sapta \xt 1--12…®n\xt* eghaghanim…®n aven, Israelia Kenan…®n nguazim ini.
\ip 2. Sapta \xt 13--22…®n\xt* eghaghanim…®n aven, me nguazim isa, Israelian anababa bar vaghvagha nguaziba ab…®gha me gan…®ngi.
\ip 3. Sapta \xt 23--24…®n\xt* eghaghanim…®n aven, Josua uan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar abuananabagh amima, Israelia Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim, ua gavgavim a gan…®di. Guizbang…®ra, God bar uan gavgavir ekiam azenara men akaz…®ma, bizir kam bang…®n, me zurara God…®n g…®n mangasa akam ak…®ri.
\ip Ez…® Josuan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar abuananam…®n, a bizir God uan agharir gavgavim…®n ingarizibagh n…®ghn…®si. God Abraham ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, nguazir kam an a is…® Abraham…®n ovavir boribar an…®ngam. Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n an gun m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fan aghuagh…®va derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, ia god…®n manam…®n ziam fam? Ez…® na ko, nan d…®penim…®n itir darazi bar mogh…®ra, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziamra fam.‚Äù (Sapta \xt 24:15\xt*) Kar bar ak…®nafarir kam…®n n…®ghn…®zir bar ekiar faragha zuim.
\c 1
\ms1 Israelia Kenan…®n nguazim Ini
\mr (Sapta 1--12)
\s1 Israelia Kenan…®n nguazim iniasa
\p 
\v 1 Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim. Ez…® gumazim Nun…®n otarim Josua, a Moses…®n akurvasi. Ez…® Moses aremez…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei,
\v 2 ‚ÄúNan ingangarir gumazim Moses, an areme. Ez…® n…® Israelian gumazamiziba dat…®r…®gh…®n me inigh, ia Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…®, k…® ia dan…®ngamin nguazim…®n otifigh.
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3-5 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:24-25\x*K…® Moses ko akam ak…®righa g…®vagha ghaze, nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n arua zuir kaba, k…® bar da is…® ia dan…®ngam.
\v 4 Nguazir ia iniamin kam…®n m…®taghniaba, da saut…®n amadaghan gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim ikegh mang…®, not…®n amadaghan Lebanon…®n kantrin m…®ghs…®abar otogham. Egh mang…® aruem anadi nagh…®n Yufretis…®n Faner ekiam…®n otogh, mang…® Hitian nguaziba bar ada inigham. Egh mang…® aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n otogham.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt God…®n Araziba 31:6-8; Hibru 13:5\x*Eght…® n…® Josua, K…® Moses ko ikez…® mogh…®ra, k…® n…® ko ikiam. K…® zurara n…® ko ik…®, egh n…® ategh mangan kogham. N…® nguazim…®n angam…®ra ikiamin dughiam…®n, gumazir taba n…® m…®sogh n…® ab…®raghan kogham.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 31:6-7; 31:23\x*‚ÄúN…® m…®t…®gh gavgafigh, egh akongan mark…®. N…® gumazamizir kaba inigh mang…®t…®, me nguazir kam iniam. K…® fom…®ra nguazir kam me a iniasa, k…® men inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®righa g…®fa.
\v 7 N…® m…®t…®gh bar gavgavigh akongan mark…®. Egh bar derav…®ra nan Akar Gavgaviba, dar g…®n mang…®. Akar Gavgavir kaba, nan ingangarir gumazim Moses, faragha n…® gan…®ngi. N…® guizbang…®ra bar adar g…®n mang…®va, egh tuavir agharir k…®riam…®n zuiba ko tuavir agharir guvim…®n zuiba dar mangan mark…®. Ia bar Akar Gavgavir kabar tam…®n tuavim atagh…®raghan mark…®. N…® kamagh…®n damuva, n…® danganir manam…®n mangam, n…® os…®mt…®zir tam batoghan kogh, derav…®ra ikiam.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Onger Akaba 1:2-3\x*N…® Akar Gavgavir kabar Ak…®nafarim bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, n…® arueba ko d…®magariba bar derav…®ra Akar Gavgavir kabar gan…®va, dar pon…®va dagh n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ik…®, egh bar dar amu. Egh n…® kamagh…®n damut…®, bizir igharazir n…® g…®n damuamiba deragh kamagh…®ra ikiam.
\v 9 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, k…® n…® m…®kemegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® m…®t…®gh gavgavigh atiatingan mark…®. Egh n…® managh mangam, k…® uaghan n…® ko mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n gumazamizibar gumazir dapanibav gei,
\v 11 ‚ÄúIa danganir e itir kam…®n aven daruva, gumazamizibav k…®mt…®ma me uari bagh daghetaba isamigh, biziba ak…®right…®, da ik…®. Aruer pumuning g…®vaght…® m…®kezim…®n, e Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mang…®va Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e dan…®ngamin nguazim iniam. Eght…® nguazir kam, kar en nguazimra.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12-15 \xt D…®boboniba 32:28-32; God…®n Araziba 3:18-20; Josua 22:1-6\x*Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n Ruben…®n anabam ko Gat…®n anabam ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam, me m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 13 ‚ÄúIa bar derav…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, ia m…®kemezir akabagh n…®ghn…®gh. A ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Jordan…®n Faner m…®riam…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n itir nguazim ia dan…®ngam. Eght…® ia an ik…® derav…®ra navir am…®rizim…®n ik…® avughsam.
\v 14 Moses, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n nguazir vuer kam, an aruem anadi nagh…®n itir nguazim, a ia gan…®ngi. Eght…® ian amuiroghboriba ko as…®ziba an ikiam. Eght…® ian m…®dorozir gumaziba, me bar uan m…®dorozir biziba inigh Jordan…®n Fanem giregh vong…®n mang…® uan aveghbuabar faragh mang…®. Egh men akuragh m…®dorozim damu.
\v 15 Ia me ko kamagh…®ra damu mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gan…®dir nguazir kam, me bar mogh…®ram an danganiba bar a da inigh, dar apiagham. Eght…® ia g…®n uamategh uan nguazim…®n izam. Kar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, ia gan…®ngizir nguazim, a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n iti, ia a dapiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® gumazir kaba Josuan akam baregha ghaze, ‚ÄúOre, bizir n…® e m…®kemeziba e bar mogh…®ra dar amuam. Ez…® danganir n…® e amadiba e bar dar mangam.
\v 17 E n…® m…®geir akaba bar mogh…®ra dar g…®n mangam, mati e faragha zurara Moses…®n akabar g…®n zui. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moses ko ikez…® mogh…®ra n…® ko ikiam.
\v 18 Eght…® tina n…®n akam barazir puvat…®, an aremegham. N…®n akam batozir gumazamiziba, me ar…®m…®ghiram. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® tugh gavgavigh atiatingan mark…®!‚Äù
\c 2
\s1 Josua gumazir pumuning amadaz…® aning ghua Jerikon nguibam, mogomem…®n an gari
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Hibru 11:31; Jems 2:25\x*Dughiar kam, Israelia Sitim…®n nguibam…®n ikiav…®ra ikia, Nun…®n otarim Josua gumazir pumuning amada, eght…® aning mang…® modogh Jerikon nguibam, ko nguazir an borogh…®n itibar ganam. Ez…® aning ghua tuavim…®n amizir mam…®n d…®penim…®n oto. Amizim…®n ziam Rahap, aning an d…®penim…®n iti.
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® gumazir maba aning baregha ghua kamagh…®n Jerikon atrivim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® derav…®ra ganigh. Israelian gumazir maba dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®mangan iza en nguibam…®n aven ikiava mogomem…®n an gari.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n oregha gumazir maba amadaz…®, me ghua Rahap m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir mogomebar en kantrin ganasa izeziba, me n…®n d…®penim…®n iti. N…® me amadaght…® me azenan iz…®. E fo, me en kantrin averiam bar mogomebar an ganasa ize.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Guizbang…®ra, Rahap gumazir kamning modo. Egha atrivim amadazir gumazibagh ifara ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, gumazir maba nan d…®penim…®n ize. Ez…® k…® me g…®fozir puvat…®, me ti nguibar manam…®n ikegha ize.
\v 5 Me guarat…®zim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akar ekiam asasava amima, gumazir kaba ua danganir kam ategha ghue. K…® fozir puvat…®, me manmagh…®ra ghue. Ia ti zuam…®ra men g…®n mang…®va me batogham.‚Äù
\v 6 Guizbang…®ra, Rahap ifaragha Israelian gumazir kamning inigha d…®penim…®n uanaga ghuriam…®n bar p…®n dadar ik…®ziba itibar apengan aning modo.
\v 7 Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba Rahap…®n akam baregha nguibar ekiam ategha zuima, nguibam…®n tiar akam…®n garir gumaziba zuam…®ra nguibam…®n tiar akam asara. Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba ghua gumazir moga garimning buri. Me aning buria arua ghua Jordan…®n Faner m…®riam…®n oto.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Israelian gumazimning t…®ghar dakuasava amima, Rahap aning iti nagh…®n p…®n ghuavanabo.
\v 9 Egha kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kantrin kam isa Israelia ian agharim gat…®. Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra gua m…®gei, atiatir bar ekiam en itima, agorogem e m…®sozima, aghariba en am…®ra.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Ua Me Ini 14:21; D…®boboniba 21:21-35\x*E kamagh…®n oraki, ia Isip…®n kantri ategha izir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Ongarir Aghevim gamiz…®, a dakez…®, ia a giregha azenan ize. Egha e uaghan kamagh…®n oraki, ia Amorian atrivir pumuning, Sihon ko Ok, ia aning…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba sara Jordan…®n Faner vuem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 11 E m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha bar ian atiatigha ikia, en aghariba en am…®ra. E dat…®r…®gh…®n gavgaviba bar puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, ian God, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an overiar p…®n itim ko nguazim…®n God.
\v 12 Kamagh…®n k…® guan azangs…®si, dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, k…® faragha derav…®ra gua gamiz…® mogh…®n, gua nan adarazi deragh me damu. Egh gua akar d…®k…®r…®zim na koma a damuva, ababanir tam nan akaght…® k…® fogh suam, gua guizbang…®ra deragh e damuam.
\v 13 Ia nan afeziam ko amebam, ko nan doziba ko nan afumiba ko men adarazi bar me ateght…®, me angam…®ra ik…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® gumazimning kamagh…®n amizim…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGa n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, damighan koght…®, God mar ga gas…®ghas…®kigh. Eght…® n…® bizir ga amizibar gun m…®kemeghan koght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nguazir kam e dan…®ngamin dughiam, ga guizbang…®ra n…® gin…®r…®gh n…®n kuarkuvigh deraghv…®ra n…® damuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Rahap…®n d…®penim bar nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazir ekiam…®n poroghav iti, ez…® an windua d…®vazir ekiam gis…®rara iti. Ez…® Rahap benir mam inigha d…®penim…®n aven a ikegha, winduan anekuniz…®, a d…®vazir ekiam…®n azenan iraghu. Egha gumazimning amadaz…®, aning benir kam…®n suigha azenan ghuaghiri.
\v 16 Ez…® Rahap kamagh…®n gumazimning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n m…®ghs…®abar modogh. Eght…® gumazir gua buriba ua Jerikon izeght…®ma, gua uamategh uan adarazi bagh mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® gumazimning kamagh…®n Rahap m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n n…® biziba bar dar amight…®, ga n…® ko d…®k…®r…®zir akatam abighan kogham.
\v 18 N…® deragh oragh, Israelia iz…® nguibar kam…®n otivamin dughiam…®n, n…® benir aghevir ga n…® gan…®dir kam, is…® uan winduan ga izaghir…®zir kam…®n aneguragh. Egh n…® uan afeziam ko amebam ko doziba ko afumiba ko uan adarazi bar me inigh uan d…®penim…®n aven me akufagh.
\v 19 Ian tav d…®penim ategh…®va nguibam…®n otogh azenan tuavim…®n mang…®t…®, me a m…®sueght…® an aremegham, kar an os…®mt…®zim. Eght…® d…®penim…®n aven iti tav aremeght…®, ga an os…®mt…®zim ateram.
\v 20 Eght…® n…® bizir ga amizir kabar gun Jerikoia m…®kemeght…®, ga n…® ko d…®k…®r…®zir akar kaba puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Rahap kamagh…®n aning ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAre. K…® gua m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra damuam.‚Äù A kamagh…®n aning m…®kemegha aning amadaz…® aning zuima, a benir aghevir kam inigha uan d…®penim…®n winduan anegura.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® gumazir kamning ghua aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n m…®ghs…®abar modoghav iti. Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba aning buria aning…®n apizir puvat…®gha, uamategha Jerikon ghue.
\v 23 Ez…® gumazir kamning g…®n m…®ghs…®aba ategha, Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n ghua Nun…®n otarim Josua batogha, bizir otivizir kabar gun a m…®gei.
\v 24 Aning kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nguazir kam bar e ganigha g…®fa. Gumazamizir an itiba bar en atiatigha aghariba men am…®ra.‚Äù
\c 3
\s1 Israelia Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mangasa
\p 
\v 1 Egha bar m…®zaraghara, Josua Israelia ko d…®kavigha, Sitim…®n danganim ategha ghua, Jordan…®n Faner m…®riam…®n danganim aghuigha iti. Me t…®ghar fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mangam.
\v 2 Aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n g…®n, gumazir dapaniba danganir me itim…®n averiam garuava kamagh…®n gumazamiziba bar me m…®gei,
\v 3 ‚ÄúIa gant…®, Livain adarazir ofa gamir gumaziba, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupugh mang…®t…®, ia danganir kam ategh men g…®rara mang…®.
\v 4 Ia faragha kagh izezir puvat…®, kamagh…®n, me faragh mang…® tuavim ian akakagham. Egh ia mang…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n borogh…®ram a t…®vagh mangan mark…®. K…® bar ian anogoroke. Ia kilomitan vam…®ra a danigh an g…®rak…®rang…®n ik…® mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa uarira uari ak…®r…®va, God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ik…®. Ia gan, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gurumzaraghan d…®gavir kuram gamir biziba ian tong…®n dar amuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Egha g…®n Josua ofa gamir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupugh gumazamizibar faragh mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® me a gupugha men faragha zui.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n k…® Israelian damazim…®n n…®n ziam f…®t…®, me kamagh…®n fogham, k…® fom…®ra Moses ko ikez…® mogh…®n, k…® n…® ko ikiam.
\v 8 Eght…® n…® kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupuziba me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa mang…® Jordan…®n Faner m…®riam…®n otivigh, egh tong s…®vagh mang…® d…®pam…®n aven pura tuivigh ik…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Josua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa rogh…®ra iz…®va Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an akam baragh.
\v 10 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n gant…®ma, God en akuragh Kenania, Hitia, Hivia, Peresia, Girgasia, Amoria, ko Jebusia me batuegham. Ia tuavir kam…®n God…®n gavgavim…®n ganigh fogh suam, Angam…®ra Itir God, guizbang…®ra en tong…®n iti.
\v 11 Egh ia dat…®r…®gh…®n gant…®, nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba, bar me gativamin Ekiam, an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam ian faragh mang…®, Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®ght…®ma d…®pam bigh…®r…®gham.
\v 12 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n 12pla gumaziba, vaghvagh Israelian anabar 12pla, me a m…®sefegh.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13-17 \xt Ua Me Ini 14:22; 14:29; 15:8\x*Egh ofa gamir gumaziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupugh mangam. Egh me mang…® men dagariba Jordan…®n Fanem…®n mag…®r…®t…®, d…®pam dutugh ua ivemaran kogham, eght…® agharir guvim…®n amadaghan izaghirir d…®paba, buigh…®va ghuavanang m…®ghs…®am…®n m…®n tugh…®v ikiam.‚Äù Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiar kam…®n God, a nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar me gativamin Ekiam.
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Israelia danganir me itim ategha Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gh mangasa zui. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupugha men faragha zui.
\v 15 Dughiar kam, me dagher igiaba asir dughiam, ez…® Jordan…®n Fanem aperiar bar ekiaba otifi. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ghua faner m…®riam…®n otivigha, uan dagariba isa d…®pam gaghui.
\v 16 Ez…® d…®pam bar p…®righa ivemari puvat…®gha, buigha m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n m…®n tughav iti. Fanem bua ghuavanaga Adam…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu, a Saretan nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n itir nguibam. Ez…® fanem…®n d…®par ivemara Amangs…®zim Itir D…®par Akarem…®n zuim, a bar m…®s…®ngi. Ez…® gumazamiziba fanem…®n vong…®n ghua Jerikon nguibam…®n borogh…®n oto.
\v 17 Ofa gamir gumaziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupugha Jordan…®n Faner torim m…®tivigha mamagh…®ra itima, Israelian gumazamiziba nguazir dak…®rt…®zim…®n ghua fanem…®n vong…®n otifi.
\c 4
\s1 Israelia Gilgal…®n dag…®ar 12pla uarigh is…®n afe
\p 
\v 1 Israelian gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n ghuez…®ma, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei,
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® Israelian anabar 12plan aven vaghvagh 12plan gumaziba, am…®sefegh.
\v 3 Egh me m…®kemeght…® me ua mang…® ofa gamir gumaziba, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n tong…®ra tuivigha ikez…® nagh…®n, dag…®ar 12pla inigh. Egh dag…®ar kaba inigh danganir ia d…®mangan ikiamim…®n mang…®.‚Äù
