\v 21 Egha Josua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúG…®n izamin dughiam…®n, ian ovavir boriba uan afeziabar azangam, ‚ÄòMe tizim bagha dag…®ar kaba kagh ada ar…®ki?‚Äô
\v 22 Eght…® men afeziaba kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòDag…®ar kaba, kar Jordan…®n Fanem dakez…® nguazim otoz…®, Israelia d…®pam abigha iza vong…®n otivizir dughiam…®n ababanim.‚Äô
\v 23 K…® dag…®ar kaba kagh ada ar…®ki, da kamak…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, fom…®ra Ongarir Aghevim gamiz…®, a dakez…® ia iza vong…®n izez…® mogh…®n, a Jordan…®n Fanem gamiz…® a dakez…® ia iza vong…®n otifi.
\v 24 Ez…® danganiba bar dar gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God amizir bizibar gan an gavgavim g…®foghasa, a bizir kabagh ami. Eght…® ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, an atiating an apengan ik…®, egh an ziam f…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\c 5
\s1 Israelia Gilgal…®n m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghori
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Amorian atrivir Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itiba, ko Kenanian atrivir Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n m…®riam…®n itiba, uaghan kamagh oraki, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia bagha Jordan…®n Fanem gamiz…®, a dakez…®, me vong…®n ghue. Bizir kam me gamiz…®, me Israelian atiatia naviba me ginivima, agharapaniba bar men am…®raz…® me iti.
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® dughiar kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® dag…®abar asiatabar ingarigh da am…®neght…® da bar ghumight…®, n…® Israelian gumazir faragha m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorezir puvat…®ziba, n…® dar aghoregh.‚Äù
\v 3 Ez…® Josua dag…®abar asiar dozibar ingarigha, m…®ghs…®ar dozir mam…®n Israelian gumazibar m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghore. M…®ghs…®ar kam, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, M…®ghs…®ar M…®karzir Mogomebar Iniba Aghorim.
\p 
\v 4 Josua bizir m…®ngarir kam bagha men, m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghori. Gumazir Isip…®n kantri ategha iziba, me gumazir m…®dorozim damuamin fofozim itiba, me bar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ariaghire.
\v 5 Gumazir Isip…®n kantri ategha azenan iziba, me bar men m…®karzir mogomebar inibar aghore. Ez…® otarir amebaba gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n oteziba, me t…®ghar men m…®karzir mogomebar inibar aghoram.
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt D…®boboniba 14:28-35\x*Fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God men inazir afeziaba bagha akam ak…®ra ghaze, a nguazir bar aghuim me dan…®ngam, eght…® nguazir kam, biziba an ik…® aghung bar deraghv…®ram otivam. Ez…® me Isip ategha men av…®riba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ez…® God ghaze, gumazir akaba batozir kaba, merara nguazir bar aghuir kam…®n ganighan kogham. Kamagh…®n, Israelia 40plan azenibar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim tintinibar arua ghua, gumazir m…®dorozim damuamin fofozim itiba, me bar mogh…®rama ariaghire.
\p 
\v 7 Me fom…®ra gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n zuir dughiam…®n, men otarir men danganiba iniamiba, me men m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, Josua dat…®r…®gh…®n men m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghori.
\v 8 Me danganir kam…®n gumazibar m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghore, egha Israelia danganir kam…®n ikiav…®ra itima gumazibar duaba m…®s…®ngi.
