\c 6
\s1 Jerikon nguibar ekiam bar mogh…®ra ikufi
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n Israelia Jerikon nguibam…®n borogh…®ra ize, kamagh…®n amiz…® Jerikon atrivim, nguibam…®n aven zuir tiar akam pamtem…®n anesara. Eght…® gumazamiziba an aven iz…®, azenan mangan kogham.
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. K…® Jerikon nguibam ko, an atrivim ko, an m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, da is…® n…® dan…®ngam.
\v 3 N…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko dughiar vam…®ran Jerikon nguibam gighuv daru. Egh ia 6plan aruebar kamagh…®ra damu.
\v 4 Egh ofa gamir gumazir 7pla m…®kemeght…®, me vaghvagh s…®ghar sipsip…®n apuribar kombar ingariziba inigh, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n faragh mang…®. Eght…® namba 7 aruem…®n, n…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko 7plan dughiabar nguibam gighu daru. Eght…® ofa gamir gumaziba me s…®ghabagh ivi ia ko nguibam gighu daru.
\v 5 Egh n…® oraght…® ofa gamir gumaziba s…®ghabagh ivit…® dar arareba mang…® ruaraght…®, ia bar mogh…®ra bar pamten tiariba akar d…®mt…®, nguibar ekiar kam…®n d…®vazim bar akarighiregham, eght…® m…®dorozir gumaziba bar mogh…®ra Jerikon nguibam…®n aven mang…®.‚Äù
