\v 6 Ez…® Nun otarim Josua, ofa gamir gumazibar diaz…® me izima, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam inigh a gisaghpugh. Egh 7plan ofa gamir gumaziba s…®ghaba ater Boksiam…®n faragh mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Egha g…®n Josua gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…®. Ia mang…®va Jerikon nguibam gighu darut…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam, an faragh mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® me Josua m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami. Egha ofa gamir gumazir 7pla ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n faragha ghua, uan s…®ghabagh ivi. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir maba Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupugha men g…®n zui.
\v 9 M…®dorozir gumazir maba, ofa gamir gumazibar faragha zui, ez…® marazi Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n g…®n zui. Egha me zuir dughiam…®n 7plan ofa gamir gumaziba s…®ghabagh ivi.
\v 10 Josua faragha gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa d…®m n…®g…®nim damu bizitam m…®k…®man mark…®, mang…® dughiar k…® d…®ms…® akar gavgavim ia dan…®ngam. Dughiar kamra, ia pamtem d…®mam.‚Äù
\v 11 Kamagh…®n, Josua ofa gamir gumaziba amadaz…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gupugha, Jerikon nguibam dughiar vam…®ran a gighuagha arui. Egha uamategha iza d…®magarim…®n, danganir me itim…®n iti.
\p 
\v 12 Egha Josua bar m…®zaraghara d…®kaviz…®, ofa gamir gumaziba ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam gupugha zui.
\v 13 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir 7pla s…®ghar 7pla givia, ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam…®n faragha zui. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir maba ofa gamir gumazibar faragha zuima, marazi g…®n iti. Ez…® s…®ghabar ararem ghuav…®ra iti.
\v 14 Me aruer pumuning…®n kamagh…®ram amigha, uamategha iza danganir me itim…®n otifi. Me 6plan aruebar kamagh…®rama ami.
\p 
\v 15 Am…®nim tiraz…® kar aruer namba 7…®n aruem, me d…®kavigha Jerikon nguibam…®n ghua faragha amiz…® mogh…®n uam a gighuagh arui. Egha aruer kamra, me 7plan dughiabar a gighuagh arui.
\v 16 Me a gighuagha arua ghua namba 7…®n dughiam…®n, ofa gamir gumaziba s…®ghabagh ivima, Josua kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, nguibar kam isa en agharim gat…®gha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n, ia pamten tiariba akar.
\v 17 E nguibar ekiar kam ko an aven itir biziba e bar dagh as…®ghas…®gham. E ofan mam…®n m…®n bar da is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngam. Eght…® Rahap, dag…®aba bagha gumaziba ko akuir amizir kam. A gumazir e Jerikon nguibam g…®fofoghasa amadaz…®mning modo. Kamagh…®n a uan adarazi ko, e me m…®sueght…® me aremeghan kogham.
\v 18 Ia oragh. Ia nguibam…®n bizir as…®ghas…®ghizitam inigh kagh izan, k…® bar ian anogoroke. Ia bizitam inigh kagh izeght…®, os…®mt…®zim ko dughiar kuram Israelia itir danganim…®n otogham.
\v 19 Bizir me silva ko gol ko bras ko ain…®n ingariziba, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizibara. Ia da inigh iz…® an dag…®ar d…®penim…®n dar ar…®kigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 6:20 \xt Hibru 11:30\x*Josua akar kaba me ganigha g…®vaz…®, ofa gamir gumaziba s…®ghabagh ivima, gumazamiziba oregha bar pamten tiariba akarima, Jerikon nguibam…®n d…®vazir gavgavim akaraghire. Ez…® gumaziba magh…®ra bar aven ghuegha uari bagha nguibam ini.
\v 21 Egha me Jerikon gumazamiziba, m…®dorozir sababar bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha men gumazir igiaba ko ghuriba sara me, me m…®sozi me ariaghire. Egha uaghan men as…®ziba sara m…®soghez…® da ariaghire.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Josua faragha Jerikon nguibam modogh an ganasa amadazir gumazimning m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa faragha akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, gua aven mang…®, amizir dag…®aba bagha gumaziba ko akuim, an d…®penim…®n mang…® a ko an adarasi, me inigh azenan izegh.‚Äù
\v 23 Ez…® gumazir igiar faragha moga nguibam…®n ganizimning aven ghua Rahap ko, an afeziam ko amebam ko, an doziba, ko an adarasi, bar me inigha azenan izegha me isava Israelia itir danganim…®n azenan me at…®.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® g…®n me nguibam avim a gat…®z…®ma a isima, an aven itir biziba bar mogh…®ra isi. Egha me nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir silva, gol, bras ko ain…®n maba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dag…®ar d…®penim…®n aven da ar…®ki.
\v 25 \x - \xo 6:25 \xt Hibru 11:31\x*Ez…® amizir dag…®aba bagha gumaziba koma akuir kam Rahap, a faragha gumazir moga Jerikon ganasa ghuzir pumuning modo. Kamagh…®n, Josua a ko an adarazi ataghiz…® me ikia iza, dat…®r…®gh…®n Rahap…®n ovavir boriba Israelian aven ikiav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 6:25 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam ‚Äúiza dat…®r…®gh…®n,‚Äù a dat…®r…®gh…®n en dughiam m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazim ak…®nafarir kam osirizir dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 6:26 \xt 1 Atriviba 16:34\x*Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Josua akar gavgavim isa gumazamizibagh an…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam ua Jerikon nguibar kam…®n ingaright…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a gas…®ghasigham. A ua nguibar kam…®n ingangaritam damight…® a d…®kavight…®, an otarir ivariam ovengam. Egh a nguibar kam…®n tiar akar ekiabar ingart…®, an otarir abuananam ovengam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Josua ko ikiav…®ra iti, kamagh…®n gumazamizir kantrin kam…®n danganiba bar dar itiba, bar mogh…®ra iza ziar ekiam isa Josua gan…®di.
\c 7
\s1 Akan arazir kuram gami
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, faragha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Israelia Jerikon nguibam d…®kab…®ragh…®va, anogoroghezir bizitam inian kogham. Ez…® Israelia akar kam batoke. Karmin otarim Akan, bizir maba ini. Karmi a Sapdin otarim, ez…® Sapdi a Seran otarim, a Judan anabam…®n mav. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n navim bar Israelia bagha pamten an isi.
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® Josua Jerikon nguibam…®n borogh…®n ikia gumazir maba amangiz…®, me Ain nguibam…®n ghue. Ain nguibam, a Betel…®n nguibam…®n amadaghan, aruem anadi nagh…®n iti. A Betaven…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n iti. A danganir kam…®n, modogh daru an ganasa me m…®gei. Ez…® me ghua Ain nguibam…®n garagha arui.
\p 
\v 3 Egha gumazir kaba g…®n uamategha iza Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bar m…®dorozir gumaziba amangight…® me mangan mark…®. N…® 2,000 o 3,000…®n m…®dorozir gumazibara amangight…® me mavanang Ain gumaziba ko m…®sogh. Ai, a nguibar ekiam puvat…®. N…® m…®dorozir gumazir av…®riba amangan mark…®.‚Äù
\v 4 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Josua Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir 3,000…®n gumazibara amangiz…® me Ain nguibam…®n ghuavanangi. Ez…® Ain gumaziba men ag…®nt…®zi me zuam…®ra ua izaghire.
\v 5 Ain m…®dorozir gumaziba uan nguibam…®n d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n ikegha Israelian, ag…®nt…®gha ghua dag…®aba ab…®zir danganim…®n tu. Egha m…®ghs…®am…®n zuir tuavim…®n uaghiri. Me 36plan Israelian gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® Israelian gavgaviba bar g…®vaz…® me bar atiatingi.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Josua bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha bar osemegha uan korotiam abigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n guam…®n ir…®gha, uan guam isa nguazim gat…®. Ez…® Israelian gumazir dapaniba me uaghan Josua ko iregha, kamagh…®ra ikiavti aruem iraghu. Egha me uan os…®mt…®zim akakaghasa nguazir m…®nemniaba isa uan dapanibagh aghui.
\v 7 Ez…® Josua ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, n…® tizim bagha e inigha Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n danganir kam…®n ize? N…® ti e is…® Amorian agharim dat…®ght…® me bar e gas…®ghas…®ghasa? N…® e ateght…® e Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®ra ikian aghua?
\v 8 O Ekiam, k…® ua manmagh…®n m…®k…®mam? Israelia apanibar atiatigha uam ekuigha ara ize.
\v 9 \x - \xo 7:9 \xt Ua Me Ini 32:12; God…®n Araziba 9:28\x*Eght…® Kenanian gumaziba ko nguibar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba bar bizir kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baragham. Egh me ti e ek…®arugh bar e m…®sueght…® e ar…®m…®ghiregh, nguazir kam…®n ziaba ua puvat…®gham. Egh me ti n…® d…®pova n…®n ziar ekiam ab…®ragham. N…® uan ziar ekiam bagh n…®ghnigh bizir tizim damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kafigh. N…® tizim bagha nguazim gir…®ghav iti?
\v 11 Israelia arazir kuram gamigha g…®fa. K…® faragha Jerikon nguibam…®n biziba inian men anogoroke, ez…® me nan akam batoke. Egha bizir k…® as…®ghas…®ghasa m…®kemeziba, me da inigha, ifara bizir kaba, uan bizibar tong…®n da monge.
\v 12 Bizir kam bang…®n, Israelia tugh uan apaniba ko m…®soghan gavgaviba puvat…®. Me dat…®r…®gh…®n bar mogh…®ra ikuvigham, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me uan apanibar ari. Bizir k…® ian anogorogheziba, ia dagh as…®ghasighan koght…®, k…® ua ia ko ikian kogham.
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄúN…® d…®kafigh. Egh mang…® gumazamizibav kemeght…®, me uari ak…®righ zuegh, egh gurum m…®zaraghan nan damazim…®n iz…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® ghaze, Ia Israelia, bizir ia inian k…® anogorogheziba, ia da inigha g…®fa. Ia bizir kaba batueghan kogh…®va, egh uan apaniba ab…®raghan kogham.
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, ia gurum m…®zaraghan vaghvagh uan anababar aven ik…® na bagh iz…®. K…® anabar tam…®n ziam d…®boroght…® a iz…®. Egh anabar kam…®n aven itir ik…®zibar gan…®va, ik…®zir tam…®n ziam d…®boroght…®, a iz…®. Egh ik…®zir kam…®n aven itir darazir gan d…®penibar aven itir darazi d…®pont…®, me iz…®. Eght…® g…®n d…®penir kam…®n itir gumaziba uaghan vaghvagh bar na bagh iz…®.
\v 15 Eght…® bizir k…® anogoroghezir kaba inizir gumazim, ia an suiragh, a ko an amuiroghboriba sara, me daboroght…®, me isigh ar…®ghiregh. Egh an biziba bar da sara, uaghan da tueght…® da isigh. Gumazir kam a bar arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a gami, ez…® Israelia aghums…®zir bar ekiam ini. Egha nan gumazamiziba na ko d…®k…®r…®zir akam ab…®ki.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…® m…®zaraghara, Josua Israelia m…®geima, me vaghvagha uan anababar aven izi. Ez…® a Judan anabam faragha me am…®sevez…® me izi.
\v 17 Ez…® a Judan anabam…®n ik…®zibar diaz…® me izima, a Seran ik…®zim…®n dia. Egha Seran ik…®ziba vaghvagh men deima me izima, a Sapdin adarazir suira.\f + \fr 7:17 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 18 Egha Josua Sapdin adarazi vaghvagha men deima, me izima, an Akan…®n suira. Akan Karmin otarim, egha Sapdin igiavotarim, egha Seran ovavir borim, a Judan anabam…®n iti.
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n Akan m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan otarim, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, n…® an damazim…®n m…®t…®gh, egh bizir n…® amizim dat…®r…®gh…®n an gun na m…®k…®m. Egh bizitam…®n nan ghuangs…®ghan mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Akan a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, k…® an damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizir amizim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.
\v 21 E m…®dorozim gamua biziba isir dughiam…®n, k…® Babilonia ingarizir korotiar bar aghuir mam ko, silvan maba ko gol…®n dag…®ar ekiam ini. Silvan os…®mt…®zim, 4 kilogrem…®n tu. Ez…® gol…®n os…®mt…®zim, 1kilogrem…®n tu. K…® bar dagh ifongegha da ini. Egha da inigha ghua uan purirpenim…®n aven mozim okoregha da aghuigha nguazim…®n da monge, ez…® silva bizir igharazibar apengan iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Josua gumazir maba amadaz…®, me ivemara Akan…®n purirpenim…®n ghue. Egha me gari, biziba bar Akan m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra mozim…®n aven iti, ez…® silva bar apengan iti.
\v 23 Ez…® me bizir kaba purirpenim…®n aven bar ada inigha Josua ko Israelia bagha ize. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n nguazim…®n da ar…®ki.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Josua ko Israelian gumazamiziba, me Akan ko a inizir biziba sara ini, silva ko korotiam ko gol…®n dag…®am, ko an otariba ko guiviba, an bulmakauba ko donkiba, ko sipsipba ko an purirpenim ko an biziba bar. Me da inigha Akor…®n danganir zarim…®n ghuaghiri.
\v 25 Egha Josua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmaghsua os…®mt…®zir ekiar kam inigha iza e gat…®? Dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God uaghan os…®mt…®zir ekiam n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® gumazamiziba dag…®aba inigha Akan ginivigha, an amuiroghboriba uaghan me giniviz…® me ariaghirez…®, me men biziba sara me gapongez…® me isi.
\p 
\v 26 Egha Akan…®n kuam gis…®n dag…®ar pozir dafam m…®k…®ni. Ez…® dag…®ar pozir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kamagh…®ra iti. Me kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n an…®ngagharim dat…®r…®gh…®n iraghu. Ez…® me danganir kam kamagh…®n a d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúAkor…®n danganir zarim.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:26 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, ziar kam, ‚ÄúAkor,‚Äù a mong ziar kam ko aning vorogh…®ra ghu, ‚Äúos…®mt…®zir ekiam.‚Äù Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam, ‚Äúdag…®ar pozir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kamagh…®ra iti,‚Äù a dat…®r…®gh…®n en dughiam…®n a m…®geir puvat…®. Puvat…®. A gumazim ak…®nafarir kam osirizim…®n dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\c 8
\s1 Israelia Ain nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®ki
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiating n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuan mark…®. K…® Ain nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim ko, an gumazamiziba ko, an nguaziba ko, nguibar ekiam, isa n…®n dafarim gat…®gha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n, n…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigh Ain mavanang.
\v 2 Ain atrivim ko an nguibar ekiam, n…® Jeriko ko an atrivim gas…®ghas…®ghiz…® mogh…®n, a gas…®ghas…®kigh. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, ia nguibar kam…®n as…®ziba ko an biziba uari bagh da inigh mangam. Ia nguibar ekiar kam ko m…®soghs…®, uari ak…®righ, egh faragh uan m…®dorozir gumazitaba amadaght…®, me mang…® nguibar ekiam…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n mongegh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigha me Aiba ko m…®soghasa ghuavanadi. A uan 30,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir fofozir aghuiba itiba am…®sevegha me amadaz…®ma, me d…®mangan faragha ghue.
\v 4 Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar derav…®ram oragh. Ia mang…® saghon mongegh ikian mark…®, ia nguibar ekiam…®n g…®rak…®rangra mongegh m…®soghs…® gan ik…®.
\v 5 Eght…® m…®dorozir gumazir na ko itiba, k…® me inigh e nguibar ekiam abigh mang…®s…® damuam. Eght…® Ain gumaziba e m…®soghs…® azenan iz…®t…®, e faragha amiz…® mogh…®n men aram.
\v 6 Egh e me ateght…® me fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, en ag…®ragh azenan izegh uan nguibar ekiam ategham. Eght…® e men aram. Me kamagh en ganigh suam, e faragha men arez…® mogh…®n ua men ari.
\v 7 Eght…® ia mongez…® nagh…®n ikegh azenim giregh mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, men nguibar ekiam is…® ian agharim dar…®gham.
\v 8 Egh ia nguibar ekiam inigh g…®vagh…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra ia avim a dat…®gh. K…® Akar Gavgavir kaba ia gan…®di, eght…® ia deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Josua me amadaz…®, me ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan, Ai ko Betel…®n nguibar t…®zimning…®n danganir mam…®n mongegha, m…®dorozim bagha m…®zua iti. Ez…® Josua d…®magarir kam…®n m…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba ko ikia danganir men purirpeniba itim…®n iti.
\p 
\v 10 Egha am…®mzaraghan Josua d…®kavigha, m…®dorozir gumazibar diagha me akuvagha, Israelian gumazir dapaniba ko me m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha ghua Ain nguibam bagha zui.
\v 11 Egha m…®dorozir gumazir Josua ko zuiba, me not…®n amadaghan Ain nguibam…®n tiar akar ekiam iti nagh…®n, danganim aghuigha an iti. Ez…® danganir me itim ko Ain nguibam…®n tiar akar ekiam…®n t…®zim…®n, danganir zarir mam iti.
\v 12 Josua 5,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir amadaziba me ghua danganir mam…®n mongeghav iti. Danganir kam aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan, Ai ko Betel…®n nguibar tizim…®n iti.
\v 13 Josua m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me isa danganibar me ar…®ki, m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rim me, not…®n amadaghan iti, ez…® marazi aruem uaghiri nagh…®n, nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n danganim aghuigha an iti. Ez…® Josua d…®magarir kam…®n ghua danganir zarim…®n iti.
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Ain atrivim Josuan m…®dorozir gumazibar gari, me itima, a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko zuam…®ra nguibar ekiam ategha, Israelia ko m…®soghasa Jordan…®n danganir zarim…®n zui. Me faraghav…®ra danganir kamra uariv soke. Egha Ain atrivim kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, Josuan m…®dorozir gumaziba nguibar ekiam…®n azenan mongegh ikegh an g…®rak…®rang…®n m…®sogh izam.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, atrivim gifara ua ivemara ara gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n amadaghan zui.
\v 16 Ez…® atrivim Israelian ag…®nt…®ghasa nguibar ekiam…®n tir m…®dorozir gumazibar dei, me Israelian ag…®nt…®gha ghua Ain nguibar ekiam saghuiam a gat…®.
\v 17 Ez…® Ai ko Betel…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba bar mogh…®ra nguibar ekiamning ategha Israelian ag…®nt…®gha ghue. Ez…® nguibar ekiamning…®n tiar akaba pura kuiaghiregha iti, ez…® dar ganamin gumaziba puvat…®.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan afuzim ghufegh, Ain nguibar ekiam…®n akagh. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nguibar ekiar kam is…® n…®n agharim dar…®gham.‚Äù Ez…® Josua Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
\v 19 A uan afuzim fez…®ma, m…®dorozir gumazir mongeziba, me an ganigha, zuam…®ra ivemara nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghuegha, a inigha, a gaboroz…®, a isi.
\p 
\v 20-21 Ez…® Ain gumaziba ragha uan nguibar ekiam…®n garima m…®gharim an otogha overiam…®n ghuavanadi. Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me faragha Ain gumazibagh ifarav arav ghue, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ua iza m…®gharim…®n gari a ghuavanadima me fo, Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua nguibar ekiam inigha, a gaboroz…® a isi. Ez…® Ain m…®dorozir gumaziba ar…® mang…® ovevem gitav…®raghan tuaviba bar puvat…®. Ez…® Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko uamategha iza bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 22 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghuegha a gaboroziba, me azenim giregha uaghan m…®dorozim…®n aven ghua, Aiba okarigha me m…®sosi. Egha Israelia Ain gumaziba, bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Men tarazi aregha ua itir puvat…®.
\v 23 Ez…® Ain atrivimra, an angam…®ra itima Israelia an suiragha a inigha Josua bagha ghu.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Israelia, Ain gumazir faragha men g…®nt…®gha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n, me danganir kam…®n uan apaniba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha g…®n marazi uamategha Ain ghuegha gumazamizir nar nguibar ekiam…®n aven itiba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 25-26 Josua dughiar kam…®n uan afuzim fegha Ain nguibar ekiam…®n akagha mamagh…®ra itima, gumazamiziba bar ariaghire. Gumazamizir ariaghirezibar d…®bobonim, a 12,000…®n tu.
\p 
\v 27 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, faragha Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelia Ain nguibar ekiam gas…®ghasigh uari bagh an as…®ziba ko biziba bar da iniam.‚Äù Ez…® Israelia bizir kaba bar uari bagha da ini.
\p 
\v 28 Egha Josua Ain nguibar ekiam gaboroz…® a bar sigha bar ikuvigha iti, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kamagh…®ra iti.
\v 29 Ez…® Josua Ain atrivim inigha temem…®n aneguraz…® an areme, ez…® an kuam ikia ghuavti aruem iraghu. Ez…® guarat…®zim…®n Josua gumazibav kemez…®ma, me an kuam inigha ghua Ain nguibam…®n tiar akar ekiam…®n anekuni. Egha me dag…®ar av…®riba isa an kuam gis…®n dar pozim m…®k…®ni. Dag…®ar pozir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kamagh…®ra iti.\f + \fr 8:29 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam, ‚Äúdag…®ar pozir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kamagh…®ra iti,‚Äù e dat…®r…®gh…®n itir dughiam an a m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim…®n dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\s1 Josua Ebal…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n Moses Osirizir Arazibar akaba d…®bori
\p 
\v 30-31 \x - \xo 8:30-31 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:25\x*\x - \xo 8:30-32 \xt God…®n Araziba 27:2-8\x*Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma Josua Israelia ko Ebal…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ize. Me kagh izegha, Josua uan gumazir mabav g…®a ghaze, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, a bagh ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingar. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, an e m…®kemezir mogh…®n ingar. Ez…® me Moses Osirizir Arazibar Ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir akabar g…®n ghua an ingari. Ak…®nafarim ghaze, me God bagh ofa damuamin dakozim…®n ingars…®, dag…®ar tuizim…®n d…®ghorezir dag…®aba inigh an ingaran mark…®, me dag…®ar k…®niba inigh an ingarigh. Ez…® me ofabar amuamin dakozim…®n ingari. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar uan ofan tue bar isia m…®gh…®riziba, inigha ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamua, egha uaghan God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabagh ami.
\v 32 Ez…® Israelia m…®tivighav…®ra ikia garima, Josua dag…®ar mabagh is…®n Moses Osirizir Akar Gavgaviba, da osiri.
\v 33 \x - \xo 8:33-35 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:29; 27:11-14\x*Ez…® Israelia bar, men gumazir dapaniba ko, ingangaribar faragh zuir gumaziba ko, men jasba ko, gumazamizir kantrin igharazibar izeziba, me bar ghua okoruar pumuning…®n tuifi. Israelian gumazamizir tuiviziba, marazi Gerisim…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n tuiviz…®, marazi Ebal…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n tuifi. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba, me Livain anabam…®n adarasi, me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itir Boksiam gupugha izez…®ma, Israelian okoruar pumuning…®n vong ko vong…®n tuivighav iti. Me uan guaba isa Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itir Boksiam m…®soke. Boksiar kam men torimra iti. Gumazamiziba Kenan…®n nguazim…®n otivigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, deragh me damus…®, me an ingangarir gumazim Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, me bizibar amuam.
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® me m…®tivighav…®ra itima, Josua Moses Osirizir Arazibar akaba bar, pamtem…®n dar bori. A, Israelia derav…®ra ik…® God…®n akabar g…®n mang…®t…®, a derav…®ra me damuamin akaba d…®bora, egha uaghan me God…®n akam batoght…® a ivezir kuram me dan…®ngamin akaba d…®bori.
\v 35 Josua Moses Osirizir Araziba d…®borima, Israelian gumazamiziba bar da baraki. Men amiziba ko, boriba ko, nguibar igharazibar gumazamiziba, me uaghan ikia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba baraki.
\c 9
\s1 Gibionia, Josua gifari
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® atrivir Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itiba, me m…®ghs…®abar itir danganibar atriviba ko, m…®ghs…®ar dozibar itir danganibar atriviba ko, danganir Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n m…®riam…®n ikegha ghua not…®n amadaghan Lebanon…®n nguazim…®n tuzir atriviba. Me kara: Hitian atrivim, Amorian atrivim, Kenanian atrivim, Peresian atrivim, Hivian atrivim ko Jebusian atrivim, me bar mogh…®ra Israelia amizir bizir kabar akam baraki.
\v 2 Me akar kaba baregha iza Josua ko Israelia m…®soghasa uari akufi.
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Gibeon…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamiziba me Hivian dakozim…®n aven iti. Me Josua Jerikon nguibam ko Ain nguibam gas…®ghas…®ghizir bizim baraki.
\v 4 Egha men marazi nguibar saghuiam…®n izezir gumazibar m…®n Josua gifarasa, wain…®n m…®sevir ghurir b…®aghireziba inigha ua da isami. Egha da inigha, uan m…®tarir bar ghuriba inigha, uan bizir ghuriba isa dagh aghui. Egha bizir kaba isa uan donkibagh is…®n ar…®ki.
\v 5 Me uaghan korotiar ghuriba aghui. Egha dagarir asuar ghurir d…®ghoraghireziba ua da isamigha, da aghui. Egha bret…®n m…®diarir aviaba inivizir kuraba uaghan da inigha izi.
\v 6 Dughiar kam, Josua Gilgal…®n danganim aghuigha an iti. Ez…® Gibeon…®n adarazi a bagha ghua, a ko Israelia batogha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúE nguibar saghuiam…®n ikegha iza ia ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim damigh, egh ia ko deragh dapiasa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:32; 34:12; God…®n Araziba 7:2\x*Ez…® Israelian gumaziba kamagh…®n Hivia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ti bar en borogh…®ra iti. E ia ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim damuan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® me kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúE pura n…®n ingangarir gumazibar otivigh ikiam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa taia. Ia managh…®ra ikegha izi?‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE n…®n ingangarir gumaziba bar saghon mar ikia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God barazi a bizir bar ekiaba Isip…®n kantrin, dagh ami.
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt D…®boboniba 21:21-35\x*Egha e uaghan Amorian atrivir Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n itimning, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, aning gamizir eghaghaniba baraki. Sihon, an Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim, ez…® Ok, a Basan…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim. A fom…®ra Astarot…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ike.
\v 11 Ez…® en kantrin gumazir dapaniba ko, gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n e m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa daghetaba sara inigh mang…® Israelia batogh kamagh me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúE pura ian ingangarir gumazibar ikiasa ia ko akam ak…®rasa izi.‚Äù ‚Äô
\v 12 Ia kagh bretbar ganigh, da isiav…®ra itima, e nguibam ategha ia bativasa da inigha izi. Ez…® bret…®n kaba dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®s…®ngigha aviaba dagh inifi.
\v 13 Ez…® wain…®n m…®sevir kaba uaghan kamagh…®ra ghu, dar igiabara e wain isa dagh rui. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia gan, da tintinibar b…®aghire. Ez…® en korotiaba ko dagarir asuaba, e tuavir ruarir kam…®n izima da bar d…®ghoraghire.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 9:14 \xt D…®boboniba 27:21; 1 Samuel 22:10; Aisaia 30:1-2\x*Ez…® Israelia dagher kaba inis…®, faragh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaragh egh g…®n ada iniam, me kamagh…®n amizir puvat…®.
\v 15 Ez…® Josua me angam…®ra ikiasa, me ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin akam ak…®ra navir am…®rizim me gan…®ngi. Ez…® Israelian gumazir dapaniba uaghan akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam…®n amamangat…®.
\p 
\v 16 Israelia me ko akam ak…®riz…® dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaz…®, me g…®n gumazir kabagh fo, kar men borogh…®ra iti adarazi men tong…®n iti.
\v 17 Ez…® Israelia d…®kavigha ghua aruer m…®kezim…®n men nguibar ekiabar otifi. Men nguibar ekiar kabanang: Gibeon, Kefira, Berot ko Kiriat Jearim.
\v 18 Me fo, Israelian gumazir dapaniba Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, me an ziam…®n Gibionia ko akam ak…®righa g…®fa. Kamagh…®n, Israelia me m…®soghez…® me ariaghirezir puvat…®. Ez…® Israelia uan gumazir dapaniba bizir kam bagha me gimoba men atari.
\v 19 Ez…® gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, e an ziam…®n me ko akam ak…®righa g…®fa. Egh dat…®r…®gh…®n e me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiran kogham.
\v 20 E kamagh…®n me damuam: e me ateght…® me angam…®ra ikiam. E fo, e God…®n damazim…®n me ko akam ak…®righa akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam ab…®ghan kogham. E me m…®sueght…®, me aremeght…®, God en atar…®va bar e gas…®ghasigham.
\v 21 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me angam…®ra ikiam. Eght…® e me ateght…®, me ik…®va bar e bagh daziba ab…®gh…®va, e bagh d…®paba tu da ater daruam.‚Äù Ez…® Israelia, uan gumazir dapaniba baregha me ataghiz…® me iti.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Josua Gibeonian diaz…® me izima a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa en borogh…®ra ikia, tizim bagha e gifara ghaze, e bar saghon mar ikegha ize? Bar puvat…®.
\v 23 Ia ifaraz…® bighang…®n, God paza ia damuam. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n en ingangarir gumazibar ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim bagh daziba ab…®gh…®va, d…®paba tuva da ater daruam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® me Josuan akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, e kamagh…®n oraki, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, uan ingangarir gumazim Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, ia iz…® kagh otivight…®, a nguazir kaba bar da is…® ia dan…®ngam, egh nguazir kabar itir gumazamiziba bar me gas…®ghasigham. Kamagh…®n, e ian atiatigha uari bagha n…®ghn…®gha ifavarir kam gami.
\v 25 Egha e dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n agharim…®n iti. N…® bizir tizim g…®n…®ghn…®zi a n…®n dera, n…® puram a damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Josua Gibeonian akuraz…®ma, Israelia me m…®soghez…® me ariaghirezir puvat…®.
\v 27 Ez…® Josua dughiar kam…®n me gamiz…®, me pura ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar ik…®, Israelia bagh daziba ab…®gh d…®paba tuva, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itir ofa gamir dakozim bagh ingangaribar amuam. Egha Gibeonia dat…®r…®gh…®n uaghan, Israelia uari akuva Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer danganiba bar, me dar ingangarir kam gamuav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 9:27 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam, ‚Äúdat…®r…®gh…®n uaghan,‚Äù a dat…®r…®gh…®n e itir dughiam m…®geir puvat…®. Puvat…®. A gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizir dughiam m…®gei.\f*
\c 10
\s1 Josua, Amoria m…®sogha me ab…®ra
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Jerusalem…®n Atrivim Adoni Sedek orazi, Josua Jerikon nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®ghiz…® mogh…®n Ain nguibam gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha nguibar ekiar kamning…®n atrivimning m…®soghez…® aning areme. Egha orazi Gibeonia Israelia ko akam ak…®righa uari inigha men borogh…®n ikia navir am…®rizim iti.
\v 2 Ez…® Jerusalem…®n atrivim ko an gumazamiziba Gibeonian arazim baregha, me bar atiatingi. Me fo, Gibeon…®n nguibam, an atrivim…®n itir nguibar ekiam…®n m…®n iti. Egha an ekevegha Ain nguibam bar a gafira. Ez…® an gumaziba, me bar m…®dorozim…®n fofozir gumazir aghuibara.
\v 3 Dughiar kam…®n Jerusalem…®n Atrivim Adoni Sedek, an borogh…®n itir atrivir 4pla, a me bagha akam amada. Atrivir kaba, Hebron…®n Atrivim Hoham, ko Jarmut…®n Atrivim Piram, ko Lakis…®n Atrivim Jafia, ko Eklon…®n Atrivim Debir.
\v 4 An akam me bagha anemaga ghaze, ‚ÄúGibeonia, Josua ko Israelia ko akam ak…®righa uari inigha ikia navir am…®rizim…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia iz…® nan akuragh e mang…® Gibeonia m…®sogham.‚Äù
\v 5 Ez…® Amorian atrivir 5plan kaba uari akuvagha ghua Gibeonia korogha me m…®soghasa. Atrivir kabar nguibabar kara, Jerusalem, Hebron, Jarmut, Lakis ko Eklon.
\p 
\v 6 Dughiar kam, Josua Gilgal…®n danganim aghuigha itima, Gibeonia a bagha zuam…®rama akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúO gumazir ekiam, e ian ingangarir gumaziba, e n…®n apengan iti. Ez…® n…® e ateghan mark…®, n…® zuam…®ra iz…® en akuragh! Amorian atrivir danganir m…®ghs…®abar itiba uan m…®dorozir gumaziba isafuragh, izighir…® e m…®soghasa.‚Äù
\v 7 Ez…® Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me akuvagha, deragha m…®sozir m…®dorozir gumazir aghuiba inigha, gumazir igharaziba sara inigha, me Gilgal ategha, Gibeonian akuragh m…®soghasa zui.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® men atiatingan mark…®, k…® me isa ian agharim gat…®gha g…®fa. Men tav ia ab…®raghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 9 Ez…® Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko d…®magarim…®n aghumra Gilgal ategha ghua Gibeon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Me ghuav…®ra ikia magh…®ra Amoria m…®sozima me bar d…®gavir kuram gami.
\v 10 Dughiar kam…®n Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba izima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Amoria gamiz…®, me atiatigha okam n…®ghn…®gha tintinibar ari. Ez…® Israelia Gibeon…®n nguibam…®n, Amorian av…®rim m…®soghez…® me ariaghire, egha bar men g…®nt…®gha ghua Bethoron…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n zuir tuavim…®n ghuavanabo. Me puv me m…®sogha ghua saut…®n amadaghan Aseka ko Makedan nguibamning…®n tu.
\v 11 Ez…® Amoria Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar ara Asekan nguibam…®n amadaghan uaghirima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ais…®n amozir of…®zir ekiabagh amiz…®, da dag…®abar m…®n izaghira me girima, me ariaghire. Amorian gumazir ais…®n amozir of…®ziba m…®soghez…® ariaghirezibar d…®bobonim ghuavanabo. Egha Israelia m…®soghez…® ariaghirezir gumazibar d…®bobonim gafira.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian akuraz…®, me Amoria m…®sogha me ab…®ra. Egha dughiar kamra, Josua Israelian damazim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAruem, n…® Gibeonia gis…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®. Iak…®nim, n…® Aijalon…®n danganir zarim…®n tugh…®v ik…® mamagh…®ra ik…®.‚Äù
\v 13 Ez…® aruem isiragha ikia kamagh…®ra iti, ez…® iak…®nim uan danganim…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Israelia uan apanibav sogha me ab…®ra. Ez…® me bizir kabar eghaghanim Jasar…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n da osiri. Guizbang…®ra, dughiar kam…®n, aruem isiragha p…®n ikiav…®ra ikia, ghua dughiar bar ruarim g…®vaz…®, am…®nim p…®ri.\f + \fr 10:13 \ft Fofozir gumaziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Jasar…®n Ak…®nafarim, a Israelian ak…®nafarir ghurir mam. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n bar ovenge. Ez…® e fozir pu, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar manaba an aven iti. Devit, Atrivim Sol ko Jonatan…®n apangkuvigha aning bagha ongezir igham osiri, a uaghan ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti. N…® 2 Samuel 1:17-27…®n ganigh.\f*
\v 14 \x - \xo 10:14 \xt Josua 10:42; 2 Atriviba 20:8-11; Aisaia 38:8\x*Fom…®ra ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizitam dat…®r…®gh…®n otoz…® mogh…®n otozir puvat…®. Otozir bizir kam, a kamak…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazir mam…®n akam baraki. Guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian akuragha m…®dorozir kam gami!
\p 
\v 15 Egha m…®dorozim…®n g…®n, Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ua Gilgal…®n danganir me itim…®n ghue.
\v 16 Ez…® Amorian 5plan atriviba m…®dorozim…®n tong…®n ara ghua Makedan nguibam…®n dag…®ar torir mam…®n iti.
\v 17 Ez…® gumazir maba me mongegha itir danganim…®n ganigha an gun Josua m…®keme.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Josua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa dag…®ar ekiaba poghpogh mang…® mozir akam ap…®righ. Egh gumazitaba aright…® me an gan ik…®.
\v 19 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian apaniba isa ian dafaribagh at…®gha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n ia pura ikian mark…®. Ia apanibav sogh men g…®nt…®gh mang…®v…®ra ik…®. Ia me ateght…® me mang…® uan nguibar ekiabar otivan mark…®.‚Äù
\v 20 Ez…® Josua Israelia ko men ag…®nt…®gha me m…®sogha, bar mogh…®ra me agevima, men varazira zuam…®ra ara ghua uan nguibar ekiabar aven mongeghav iti.
\v 21 Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar mogh…®ra deragha ikia iza Makedan danganir me itim…®n Josua bato. Ez…® Kenan…®n nguazim…®n iti darazi m…®g…®r…®g…®atam ua Israelia gasa me m…®geir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n uan gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® mozim…®n akam…®n itir dag…®aba poegh, 5plan atrivir kaba inigh na bagh iz…®.‚Äù
\v 23 Ez…® Josuan gumaziba, 5plan atrivir dag…®ar torim…®n aven itir kaba, me inigha azenim gat…®. Atrivir kabar nguibabar kara, Jerusalem, Hebron, Jarmut, Lakis ko Eklon.
\p 
\v 24 Me atrivir kaba inigha a bagha ghuz…®, a Israelian gumaziba bar men diagha me akufa. Egha gumazir dapanir an g…®n ghueziba, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa kagh iz…®va uan dagariba is…® atrivir kabar tuebar ar…®kigh.‚Äù Ez…® me a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® Josua Israelian gumazir dapanibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa akong…®va atiatingan mark…®. Ia tuivigh gavgafigh. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian apaniba arazir kamra me damuam.‚Äù
\v 26 Egha Josua atrivir kabav soghez…® me ariaghirez…®, a me isa temer 5plan me guiz…®, men kuaba guighav ikia ghuavti aruem g…®fa.
\v 27 Ez…® aruem iraghuz…®, a gumazibav kemez…® me atrivir kabar kuaba inigha, ghua torir me mongezir kam…®n me akuni. Egha torir kam…®n akam me dag…®ar ekiabar anep…®ri. Ez…® a dat…®r…®gh…®n ikiav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 28 Egha dughiar kamra, Josua Makedan nguibar ekiam…®n m…®dorozim gamua an atrivim…®n suiraghav a m…®soghez…® an areme. Egha uan gumazibav kemez…® me nguibar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® men tav ua itir puvat…®. A Jerikon atrivim gamizir arazir kamra, a ua Makedan atrivim gami.
\s1 Israelia nguibar ekiar igharaziba ini
\p 
\v 29 Egha bizir kabar g…®n, Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Makedan nguibam ategha ghua Lipnan nguibam…®n otogha me m…®sosi.
\v 30 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian akuraz…® me m…®dorozim gamua uan apaniba ab…®nigha, atrivim sara suiraghav a m…®soghez…® an areme. Me nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir adarasi, tarazi ataghiz…® me itir puvat…®. Me bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. A Jerikon atrivim gamizir arazir kamra, uaghan Lipnan atrivim gami.
\p 
\v 31 Bizir kabar g…®n, Josua Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigha, Lipnan nguibam ategha ghua Lakis…®n nguibam…®n otogha, a korogha me m…®sosi.
\v 32 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian akuragha Lakisia isa Josuan dafarim gat…®. Egha am…®mzaraghan a Lakis ko an aven itir adarazi bar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire. A Lipna gamizir arazir kamra, uaghan Lakis…®n adarazigh gami.
\v 33 Ez…® Geser…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Horam, a Lakis…®n akuragh m…®soghasa izi. Ez…® Josua, Horam uan adarazi ko bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\p 
\v 34 Egha bizir kabar g…®n, Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Lakis…®n nguibam ategha, ghua Eklon…®n nguibam korogha magh…®ra me m…®sosi.
\v 35 Dughiar me ghua me korozim…®n, aruer kamra, me bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Me Lakis…®n adarazigh amiz…® mogh…®n, me uaghan Eklon…®n adarazigh ami.
\p 
\v 36 Me kamagh…®n amigha g…®vagha, Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Eklon…®n nguibam ategha, ghuavanaga Hebronia ko m…®sosi.
\v 37 Me ghua me korogha magh…®ra me m…®sosi. Me atrivim ko nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir gumazamiziba bar me m…®suegha, nguibar men borogh…®n itibar gumazamiziba sara m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Me men tarazi ataghiz…® me itir puvat…®. Egha me Eklon…®n adarazigh amiz…® mogh…®n, me uaghan arazir kamra Hebron…®n adarazigh ami.
\p 
\v 38 Egha Josua Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigha, ighagh…®regha ua iza Debir…®n nguibar ekiam korogha me m…®sosi.
\v 39 Me ghua me korogha magh…®ra me m…®sosi. Me atrivim ko nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir gumazamiziba bar me m…®suegha, nguibar men borogh…®n itibar gumazamiziba sara m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Me men tarazi ataghiz…® me itir puvat…®. Egha me Lipna ko Hebron…®n atrivimning gamizir arazimra, me uaghan Debir…®n atrivim gami.
\p 
\v 40 Josua Kenan…®n nguazir vuer mam garua, an atriviba ko an gumazamiziba bar me m…®sogha me ab…®ra. Egha m…®ghs…®abar itir danganibar atrivibav sogha me ab…®nigha, Negev…®n danganim…®n itir atrivibav sogha me ab…®nigha, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itir m…®ghs…®abar atriviba bar me m…®sogha me ab…®nigha, egha Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n itir nguibabar atrivibav sogha me ab…®ni. A men tarazi ataghiz…® me itir puvat…®. A Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 41 Josua danganir kam…®n nguibar kabar gumazamiziba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. A saut…®n amadaghan itir nguibam Kades Barnean, ikegha iza Gasan nguibam…®n oto, an ongarir dadarim…®n borogh…®n iti. Egha Gosen…®n danganim…®n ikegha not…®n amadaghan iza Gibeon…®n nguibam…®n tu.
\v 42 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, a men akuraz…® me atrivir kabav sogha me ab…®nigha, men nguaziba dughiar kamra bar ada ini.
\v 43 Egha Josua Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigha iza uamategha Gilgal…®n me itir danganim…®n ghu.
\c 11
\s1 Israelia, Atrivim Jabin ko // an namakaba, me ab…®ni
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Jabin, Hasor…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim, a Israelia amizir bizibar eghaghanim baregha, nguibar ekiar kabar atriviba bagha akaba amangi, kar Madon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Atrivim Jobap ko, Simron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim ko Aksap…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim.
\v 2 Egha a uaghan not…®n amadaghan itir nguibar m…®ghs…®abar itibar atriviba bagha akam amada, egha Jordan…®n Faner zarir saut…®n amadaghan, Galilin D…®par Akarer m…®riam…®n itir atriviba bagha akam amada. Egha not…®n itir m…®ghs…®ar dozibar nguibabar atriviba bagha akam amaga, Dor…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n ongarir m…®riam…®n itir atriviba bagha akam amada.
\v 3 Egha Kenanian nguibar aruem anadi nagh…®n ko, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itiba bagha akam amada. Egha m…®ghs…®am…®n itir nguibar kabar atriviba bagh akaba amangi, kar Amoria, Hitia, Peresia ko Jebusia. Egha Hivian atriviba bagha akam amada, me Mispan nguazim…®n Hermon…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n iti.
\v 4 Ez…® atrivir kaba akar kam baregha bar mogh…®ra uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ize. Men m…®dorozir gumaziba bar av…®rasemegha, ongarir m…®riam…®n gigim…®n m…®n ghugha, hoziar av…®rim ko karis…®n av…®rim iti.
\v 5 Ez…® atrivir kaba bar mogh…®ra uan m…®dorozir gumaziba akuvagha men akua iza Merom…®n Faner m…®riam…®n danganir mam aghuigha an ti.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúGurumzaraghan dughiar kamra, k…® Israelian akuraght…® me bar uan apanibav sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® men atiatingan mark…®. Egh ia bar men hoziabar suer ag…®ribar aghoregh, men karisbar apongeght…® da isigh.‚Äù
\v 7 Ez…® men apaniba t…®ghar m…®dorozim bagha uari akuvima, Josua uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Merom…®n Faner m…®riam…®n m…®dorozim fore.
\v 8 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian akuraz…® me m…®dorozim…®n uan apaniba ab…®ra. Ez…® Israelia uan apanibav sogha men ag…®nt…®gha not…®n amadaghan ghua, Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam ko Misrefot Maim…®n nguibam…®n otogha, ghua aruem anadi nagh…®n Mispan danganir zarim…®n oto. Me m…®sogha mamagh…®ra ikia ghua uan apaniba bar me ag…®fa.
\v 9 Ez…® Josua Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n men hoziabar suer ag…®riba aghoregha men karisbagh apongez…® da isi.
\p 
\v 10 Egha Josua g…®n uamategha iza Hasor…®n nguibar ekiam inigha g…®vagha an atrivim m…®soghez…® an areme. Dughiar kam…®n Hasor…®n nguibar ekiam, a nguibaba bar dar faragha itir nguibam.
\v 11 Ez…® Israelia Hasorian gumazamiziba bar me m…®suaghar…®ki, ez…® men tav ua itir puvat…®. Ez…® me nguibar ekiar kam gaboroz…® a isi.
\v 12 Josua atriviba bar men suigha men nguibar ekiaba bar ada inigha, bar mogh…®ra me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, a m…®kemez…® mok…®n.
\v 13 Ez…® Israelia nguibar ekiar gumaziba m…®ghs…®ar dozibagh is…®n ingarizibagh apongezir puvat…®. Josua me m…®kemez…® me Hasor…®n nguibar ekiamram aboro.
\v 14 Ez…® Israelia nguibar ekiar kabar bizir aghuiba ko dag…®aba ko bulmakauba uari bagha dar suiki. Egha gumazamizitam ataghiz…® a itir puvat…®. Me bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\p 
\v 15 Ikiav…®ra Itir God faragha m…®g…®r…®g…®am isa uan ingangarir gumazim Moses gan…®ngiz…®, Moses m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba isa Josua gan…®ngi, ez…® Josua bar dar g…®n ghu. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Josua bar mogh…®ra bizibagh ami.
\s1 Josua, nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar ada ini
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Josua nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar ada ini. A danganir m…®ghs…®aba isava, Negev…®n Distrigh…®n danganiba bar ada isava, Gosen…®n Distrik ko d…®paba puvat…®zir danganim Araba isava, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n m…®ghs…®ar doziba isava, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim ini, kar bar Israelian danganir zariba ko danganir m…®ghs…®aba itiba.
\v 17-18 Nguazir kam…®n m…®taghniam, Halak…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ikegha ghua Idom…®n nguazim…®n borogh…®n saut…®n amadaghan ghua, not…®n amadaghan ghua, Lebanon…®n nguazim…®n danganir zarim…®n itir nguibam Balgat…®n oto, a Hermon…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n iti. Dughiar kam Josua, dughiar bar ruarim…®n atrivir kaba ko m…®sogha, bar me m…®suaghar…®ki.
\v 19 Ez…® nguibar igharazitam Israelia ko navir am…®rizim inizir puvat…®. Hiviara Israelia ko navir am…®rizim inigha me ko iti. Kar Gibeon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven itir adarasi. Ez…® Israelia, igharaz darazi bar mogh…®ra me gas…®ghas…®ki.
\v 20 \x - \xo 11:20 \xt God…®n Araziba 7:16\x*Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…®, men navibagh amiz…® da gavgavigha, Israelia ko m…®soghasa. Ez…® puvat…®, Israelia men apangkuvizir puvat…®. Israelia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra Moses gan…®ngizir m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n g…®n ghua, me gas…®ghasigha bar me ag…®fa.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Josua ghua Anak…®n ovavir boribar adarasi, bar me gas…®ghas…®ki. Kar gumazir ekiar bar ruariba. Me Hebron…®n nguibam, ko Debir…®n nguibam, ko Anap…®n nguibam, ko Juda, ko Israel…®n danganir m…®ghs…®ar igharazibar iti. Josua gumazir kaba bar me ag…®vagha men nguibaba sara bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki.
\v 22 Anakian tav ua Israel…®n itir puvat…®. Men varazira Gasan nguibar ekiam ko Get…®n nguibar ekiam ko Asdot…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia av…®rasemezir puvat…®.
\v 23 Ez…® Josua nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar ada ini, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra. Ez…® Josua danganir kaba tuiragha vaghvagha bar mogh…®ra Israelian anababagh an…®ngiz…®, me bar dar ghuaviba ikiangi. Kamagh…®n, m…®dorozitam ua nguazir kam…®n otivir puvat…®z…®, Israelia avughsi.
\c 12
\s1 Moses m…®dorozim…®n ab…®nizir atrivibar ziaba
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 12:1-5 \xt D…®boboniba 21:21-35; God…®n Araziba 2:26--3:11\x*Fom…®ra, Moses t…®ghar ovengamin dughiam…®n, a faragha Israelia inigha ghua, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n itir atrivimning m…®sogha, aning ab…®ragha aning…®n nguaziba bar ada ini. Nguazir kam…®n m…®taghniam, saut…®n ikegha Arnon…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n ikegha, ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n otogha, ghua not…®n amadaghan Hermon…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n tu.
\v 2 Moses m…®sogha ab…®razir atrivir mam…®n ziam, Sihon. An Amorian atrivim, egha Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam gativagha an gari. Ez…® an kantrin saut…®n itir m…®taghniam, an Arnon…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n tong…®n iti. Ez…® uaghan Arnon…®n Fanem…®n not…®n amadaghan itir nguibam Aroer, a uaghan an nguazim. Aruem anadi nagh…®n, Jabok…®n Fanem, an Atrivim Sihon garir nguazim ko Amonian nguazim ab…®ki. Egha Jabok…®n Fanem ragh…®r…®gha aruem uaghiri nagh…®n zui. Ez…® Sihon…®n nguazir not…®n itir m…®taghniam, a Jabok…®n Fanem…®n tu. An nguazir kam, a saut…®n itir Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n nguazir akuar mam.
\v 3 Sihon uaghan Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n danganir zarim…®n gari, egha Galilin D…®par Akarem iti nagh…®n ikegha ghua Bet Jesimot…®n nguibam ko Amangs…®zim Itir D…®pam…®n oto. Egha bar ghua saut…®n amadaghan Pisgan m…®ghs…®am…®n apengan tu.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® g…®n Moses ko Israelia Basan…®n nguazim…®n Atrivim Ok, a m…®sogha aneb…®ra. A Refaimbar gumazir mam, me gumazir bar ekiar ruariba, egha av…®rasemezir puvat…®. Ok, a men gumazir abuananam, egha a Astarot ko Edrein nguibamning…®n iti.
\v 5 Ez…® an ativazir nguazim…®n m…®taghniam, not…®n amadaghan Hermon…®n M…®ghs…®am itir nguazim…®n ikegha, ghua aruem anadi nagh…®n amadaghan, Salekan nguibam…®n oto. A uaghan Basan…®n Distrigh…®n danganiba bar dar gara ghua Gesur ko Makan nguazir m…®taghniar aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n itim…®n tu. A uaghan Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n nguazir not…®n itir akuar mam gativagha an gara, ghua saut…®n amadaghan Atrivim Sihon, an kantrin nguazir m…®taghniam…®n tu.
\v 6 \x - \xo 12:6 \xt D…®boboniba 32:33; God…®n Araziba 3:12\x*Ez…® Moses, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim, a Israelia ko, Sihon ko Ok m…®sogha bar aning ab…®ra. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, nguazir kam isa Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko, Gat…®n anabam…®n adarasi, ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam a me gan…®ngi.
\s1 Atriviba ko Nguibar Josua m…®dorozim gamuava ab…®razibar ziaba
\p 
\v 7 Kar nguazir kam…®n itir atriviba, Josua Israelia ko, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n amadaghan aruem uaghiri nagh…®n m…®sogha ab…®niziba. Me Lebanon…®n danganir zarim itir nguibam Balgat…®n ikegha, me m…®sogha me ab…®ra ghua Halak…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n tu, a Idom…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n iti. Josua nguazir kaba ab…®gha vaghvagha Israelian anababagh an…®di. Eght…® nguazir kaba men nguazibar m…®n ik…® kamagh…®ra ikiam.
\v 8 Kar, nguazir m…®ghs…®aba itiba, ko aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itir m…®ghs…®ar doziba, ko Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim, ko Jordan…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n itir m…®ghs…®ar muziariba, ko gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim, ko saut…®n amadaghan Negev…®n danganim. Nguazir kaba, Peresia, Hitia, Amoria, Kenania, Hivia ko, Jebusia, me faragha adar ike.
\v 9 Israelia nguibar ekiar kabar atrivibav sogha me ab…®ni, dar ziabar kara. Jerikon nguibam…®n atrivim, Betel…®n nguibam borogh…®ra itir nguibam, Ain atrivim,
\v 10 Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Hebron…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 11 Jarmut…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Lakis…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 12 Eklon…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Geser…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 13 Debir…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Geder…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 14 Horman nguibam…®n atrivim, Arat…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 15 Lipnan nguibam…®n atrivim, Adulam…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 16 Makedan nguibam…®n atrivim, Betel…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 17 Tapuan nguibam…®n atrivim, Hefer…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 18 Afek…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Lasaron…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 19 Madon…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, ko Hasor…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 20 Simronmeron…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Aksap…®n nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 21 Tanak…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, Megidon nguibam…®n atrivim,
\v 22 Kedes…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, ko Jokneam…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, nguibar kamning Karmel…®n Distrigh…®n iti.
\v 23 Egha uaghan Dor…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, an ongarir dadarim…®n borogh…®n iti, egha Goim…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, a Galilin Distrigh…®n iti.
\v 24 Egha uaghan Tirsan nguibam…®n atrivim. Israelia 31plan atriviba bar me m…®sogha me ab…®nigha men nguaziba bar ada ini.
\c 13
\ms1 Me nguaziba tuiragha Israelian anababagh an…®di
\mr (Sapta 13--22)
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, Israelia nguazir igharazir me inizir puvat…®ziba, uaghan da iniam
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® azenir av…®riba g…®vaz…®ma, Josua ikia ghua bar ghuri. Ez…® dughiar mam Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bar ghuri, egh dughiar ruarim…®n ikian kogham. Ez…® nguazir av…®riba ikiav…®ra itima, n…® t…®ghar m…®sogh…®va ada iniam.
\v 2-3 Nguazir kabanang: Filistian nguaziba bar, ko men nguibar ekiar 5plan kabanang, Gasa, Asdot, Askelon, Get, ko Ekron. Ia uaghan Gesur…®n nguaziba inizir puvat…®. A Isip…®n nguazir m…®taghniar aruem anadi nagh…®n iti. Ia uaghan saut…®n amadaghan Avia, men nguaziba inizir puvat…®. Ia uaghan, Sihor…®n Faner m…®riam…®n itir nguazim, a Isip…®n kantrin m…®taghniam…®n iti, egha not…®n amadaghan ghua Ekron…®n nguibam…®n nguazim, ia a inizir puvat…®.
\v 4 Ia Kenanian nguaziba bar t…®ghar ada iniam. Nguazir kam, a Saidon…®n nguazim…®n itir nguibam Mearan ikegha, ghua Afek…®n nguibam…®n oto, an Amorian nguazir m…®taghniam…®n iti. Ia nguazir kaba t…®ghar ada iniam.
\v 5 Ia Gebalian nguazim ko, Lebanon…®n nguazir aruem anadi nagh…®n itiba, ia bar da inizir puvat…®. Nguazir kaba, Hermon…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n itir nguibam Balgat…®n ikegha ghua Hamat…®n Tuavir Akam…®n tu.
\v 6 \x - \xo 13:6 \xt D…®boboniba 33:54\x*Ia uaghan, Saidon…®n gumazamizir Lebanon…®n M…®ghs…®abar ikia ghua Misrefot Maim…®n nguibam…®n itiba, ia men nguaziba inizir puvat…®. K…® uab…® Israelian faragh mang…® men ag…®raght…® me aregham, eght…® Israelia nguazir kaba inigh dar ikiam. K…® n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, n…® nguazir kaba bar ada abigh, da is…® Israelia danight…® me dar ik…®.
\v 7 Egh n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazir kam tuiragh a is…®, Israelian 9plan anababa ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n igharazim, bar me dan…®ngigh.‚Äù
\s1 Ruben, Gat, ko Manase, men nguaziba
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 13:8 \xt D…®boboniba 32:33; God…®n Araziba 3:12\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, a fom…®ra Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarasi, ko Gat…®n anabam…®n adarasi, ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n faragha zuim…®n adarasi, nguazir maba me ganigha g…®fa. Men nguaziba aruem anadi nagh…®n Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n iti.
\v 9 Ez…® men nguazim, an Arnon…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n tong…®n itir nguibam…®n ikegha not…®n zui. Ez…® uaghan Arnon…®n Fanem…®n not…®n m…®riam…®n itir nguibam Aroer, a uaghan men nguazim. Egha men nguazim ghua m…®ghs…®ar orazim…®n danganir bar zarir ekiam itir nguaziba inigha ghua Medeban nguibam…®n otogha ghua Dibon…®n nguibam…®n tu.
\v 10 Egha uaghan Amorian Atrivim Sihon, an nguibar ekiaba bar ada ini. Sihon fom…®ra uab…® Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, egha nguibar ekiar kabagh ativagha dar gara ghua, Amonian nguazim ko m…®taghniam at…®.
\v 11 Egha me uaghan Gileat…®n nguazim isava, Gesur ko Makat…®n Distrik sara inigha, uaghan Hermon…®n m…®ghs…®am sara, bar ada ini. Egha Basan…®n Distrigh…®n danganiba bar ada inigha, ghua Salekan nguibam…®n tu.
\v 12 Egha me, nguazir Atrivim Ok ativaziba, bar ada ini. A Refaimbar gumazir mam, me gumazir ekiar bar ruariba, egha me av…®rasemezir puvat…®. Ok, a men gumazir abuananam. A fom…®ra, Astarot ko Edrein nguibamning…®n iti. Ez…® Moses gumazir kaba ko m…®sogha me ab…®ragha bar me batoke.
\v 13 Egha Israelia, Gesur ko Makat…®n nguibamning…®n adarasi, me batoghezir puvat…®. Ez…® merara ikia dat…®r…®gh…®n Israelian tong…®n ikiav…®ra ikia kati.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 13:14 \xt God…®n Araziba 18:1\x*Ez…® fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, as…®zir gumaziba inigha iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damuasa avim…®n tueba, kar Livain anabam…®n adarazi damuamin ingangarim. K…® bizir aghuim…®n m…®n a isa me gan…®ngiz…®, me a ini. Eght…® ingangarir kam me ko ik…® kamagh…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n, Moses nguazitam isava Livain adarazigh an…®ngizir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 15 Egha Moses nguazir akuar maba isa vaghvagha Ruben…®n anabam…®n ik…®zibagh an…®ngiz…®, me dagh apiagha dagh amua iti.
\v 16 Ez…® men nguazim, an Arnon…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n tong…®n itir nguibam…®n ikegha not…®n zui. Ez…® uaghan Arnon…®n Fanem…®n not…®n m…®riam…®n itir nguibam Aroer, a uaghan men nguazim. Egha men nguazim ghua m…®ghs…®ar orazim…®n danganir bar zarir ekiam itir nguaziba inigha ghua Medeban nguibam…®n oto.
\v 17 Egha bar ghua Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha ghua, m…®ghs…®ar orazim…®n danganir bar zarir ekiam itir nguaziba, dar aven itir nguibar kaba sara ini. Dar ziabar kara: Dibon, Bamotbal, Bet Balmeon,
\v 18 ko Jahas, Kedemot, Mefat,
\v 19 ko Kiriataim, Sipma, Seretsahar, a danganir zarir kam…®n itir m…®ghs…®ar muziarim gis…®n iti.
\v 20 Egha Betpeor, ko nguibar Pisgan m…®ghs…®am…®n m…®riabar itiba, ko Bet Jesimot.
\v 21 Nguibar kaba da, m…®ghs…®ar orazim…®n danganir bar zarir ekiam itir nguaziba, dar aven itir nguibaba bar mogh…®ra. Kar Amorian Atrivim Sihon uab…® Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, egha nguibar ekiar kabagh ativagha dar gari. Moses a ko m…®sogha aneb…®ragha uaghan Midianian gumazir dapanir kabav sogha me ab…®ra. Men ziabar kara: Evi, Rekem, Sur, Hur, ko Reba. Me faragha bar mogh…®ra nguazir kam…®n apiagha itima, Atrivim Sihon ingangarim me gan…®ngiz…® me itir danganibar gari.
\v 22 Egha Beor…®n otarim Balam, a g…®n otivamin bizibar gun m…®geir gumazim, Israelia uaghan a m…®soghez…® an areme.
\v 23 Ez…® Jordan…®n Fanem, a Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarazir nguazir m…®taghniam. Nguibar ekiar kaba ko dar nguibar doziba, Ruben…®n anabam…®n ik…®ziba vaghvagha uari baghav…®ra da ini.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Moses uaghan nguazir kabar maba tuiragha vaghvagha Gat…®n anabam…®n ik…®zibagh an…®ngiz…®, me vaghvagha dagh apiaghav iti.
\v 25 Dar ziabar kara: Jaser…®n nguazim, ko Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguibar ekiaba, ko Amonian nguazim…®n akuar mam, a ghua Aroer…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu. Aroer, a Raban nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n iti.
\v 26 Egha men nguazim, Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha ghua, Ramatmispen nguibar ekiam ko Betonim…®n nguibam…®n otogha ghua, Mahanaim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha, ghua Lodebar…®n nguazir m…®taghniam…®n tu.
\v 27 Ez…® Gat…®n anabam…®n adarasi, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n itir nguibar kaba ini. Dar ziabar kara: Betharam…®n nguibam, ko Betnimran nguibam, Sukot…®n nguibam, ko Safon…®n nguibam, ko Atrivim Sihon…®n nguazir otevir mam, a Hesbon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim, a faragha an gari. Egha Gat…®n anabam…®n adarasi, nguazir Jordan…®n Faner m…®riam…®n itim inigha ghua aruem anadi nagh…®n otogha, bar ghua not…®n amadaghan Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n tu.
\v 28 Nguibar ekiar kaba ko dar nguibar doziba, Gat…®n anabam…®n ik…®zibar adarazi uari baghav…®ra da inigha dagh apiaghav iti.
\p 
\v 29 Egha Moses nguazir otevir mam isa Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mav gan…®ngiz…®, me vaghvagha uari bagha a inigha a gapia.
\v 30 Ez…® men nguazim Mahanaim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha, ghua Basan…®n Distrigh…®n danganiba bar ada ini. Atrivim Ok, a fom…®ra Basan gativagha an gari. Me uaghan 60 plan nguibar ekiar Jair gariba, da Basan…®n distrigh…®n iti, me bar da ini.\f + \fr 13:30 \ft Jair, a Manasen ovavir boribar mam.\f*
\v 31 Men nguazir kam, a Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n akuam inigha, Astarot ko Edrein nguibamning ini, Atrivim Ok, fom…®ra ativagha ganizir nguibamning. Egha Moses nguazir kam isava Manasen otarim, Makir…®n ovavir boribar ik…®zibar adarazi vaghvagha me gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 32 Kamagh…®ra, Moses Moap…®n danganir zarim…®n ikia Jerikon nguibam…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n amadaghan Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n nguazir kaba, a bar da tuiragha da isa Israelia gan…®ngi.
\v 33 \x - \xo 13:33 \xt D…®boboniba 18:20; God…®n Araziba 18:2\x*Egha Moses nguazir taba isava Livain anabam…®n adarazigh an…®ngizir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, a mati bizir aghuir ia inizim…®n m…®n iti, kamagh…®n ia nguazitam inian kogham.‚Äù
\c 14
\s1 Israelia, Kenan…®n nguaziba tuiragh uari dan…®ngasa satu gikararai
\p 
\v 1-3 \x - \xo 14:1-3 \xt D…®boboniba 26:52-56; 32:33; 34:13-15; God…®n Araziba 3:12-17\x*Kar Kenan…®n nguazir as…®zir Israelian anababa vaghvagha inizibar eghaghanim. Israelia Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Moses nguaziba isa Israelian anabar pumuning ko Israel…®n anabar mam…®n akuam gan…®ngi. Egha a nguazitam abigha Livain adarazigh an…®ngizir puvat…®.
\p Ez…® Israelia ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Kenan…®n nguazim…®n otogha g…®vagha, ofa gamir gumazim Eleasar ko Nun…®n otarim Josua, ko Israelian anababa vaghvagha men gumazir dapaniba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami. Egha nguazim tuiragh uan 9plan anababa ko anabar mam…®n akuar igharazim, me dan…®ngasa a bagha satu gikararai.
\p 
\v 4 Egha me nguazim ab…®gha gari, Josep…®n otarimning, Manase ko Efraim ik…®zir pumuning…®n m…®n iti, Manasen adarazi ko Efraim…®n adarasi. Egha me nguazitam abigha Livain anabam…®n adarazigh an…®ngizir puvat…®.\f + \fr 14:4 \ft Men inazir afeziam Jekop, a 12plan otariba iti, egha me 12plan anababagh amiz…®, da Israelian otifi. Egha g…®n Josep…®n ik…®zim, akuar pumuning…®n oto, kamagh…®n Israelia 13plan anababar otifi. Egha nguaziba tuis…®gh uari dan…®ngamin dughiam…®n, me nguazim tuiragha 12plan anababagh an…®ngi, egha me nguazir taba Livaibagh an…®ngizir puvat…®. God uab…® uan ingangarim Livai bagh an…®ngi, ez…® bizir kam mati bizir aghuim…®n m…®n me a ini. N…® Josua 13:33…®n gan.\f* Livaiba, me nguibar ekiar mabara ini, ez…® nguibar ekiar kabanang, danganir me bulmakauba ko sipsipbar ganamiba iti.
\v 5 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, Israelia Kenan…®n nguazim ab…®gha uan adarazigh an…®di.
\s1 Josua Hebron…®n nguibam isa Kalep gan…®ngi
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 14:6 \xt D…®boboniba 14:30\x*Josua nguaziba ab…®gha me gan…®dima, Judan gumazir maba iza Gilgal…®n a bagha ize. Ez…® Kenasian gumazim Jefune, an otarim Kalep, Josua bagha iza a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® fo, e Kades Barnean ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ga bagh damuamin biziba bar dar gun uan ingangarir gumazim Moses m…®keme.
\v 7 \x - \xo 14:7 \xt D…®boboniba 13:1-30\x*Dughiar kam…®n k…® 40plan azeniba itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, a na amaga ghaze, n…® Kades Barnea ategh mang…® nguazir ekiar kam mogomem…®n, a getiva an ganigh. Ez…® k…® ghua uan damazim…®n ganizir biziba, k…® uamategha iza guizbang…®ra bar uan navim sara Moses geghani.
\v 8 Ez…® nan aveghbuar na ko ghueziba, me atiatir m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh amima, atiatim gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra men navir averiabagh iz…®vagha me ab…®ni. Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan God, an akam…®n g…®n ghua uab…® isa a gan…®ngi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 14:9 \xt D…®boboniba 14:24; God…®n Araziba 1:36\x*Dughiar kam…®n, Moses na ko akam ak…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® bar derav…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, an akam…®n g…®n ghua uab…® isa a gan…®ngi, kamagh…®n n…® uan dagarim…®n d…®kagha aruizir nguazir kam, an a is…® n…® uan boriba ko ia danight…®, ia a daperagh an ik…® kamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äô ‚Äù
\v 10 Egha Kalep ua kamagh…®n Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. Israelia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir kam…®n gun Moses m…®kemez…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n 45plan azeniba g…®fa. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n azenir 85plan ikia egha ikiav…®ra iti.
\v 11 \x - \xo 14:11 \xt God…®n Araziba 34:7; Onger Akaba 18:32-34\x*Fom…®ra, Moses ingangarir kam damuasa na amadazir dughiam, k…® gavgavim iti. Ez…® gavgavir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n nan ikiav…®ra itima, k…® m…®sogh bizibar amu daruv…®ra ikiam.
\v 12 N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, na dan…®ngasa akam ak…®rizir nguazir m…®ghs…®abar itiba, n…® da is…® na dan…®ng. N…® dughiar kam…®n uab…® ikiav orazi, k…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Anakian gumazir ruarir bar ekiaba itima, men nguibaba bar ekevegha d…®vazir gavgavibar aven iti. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, na m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, na ko ik…®t…®, k…® me m…®sogh men ag…®raght…® me aregham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n oregha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, deragh Jefunen otarim Kalep damuasa God ko m…®gei. Egha a Hebron…®n nguibam isava a gan…®ngi.
\v 14 Guizbang…®ra, Kalep, a Kenasian gumazim Jefunen otarim, a bar deragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, an akam…®n g…®n ghua bar uab…® isava a gan…®ga, an g…®n zui. Kamagh…®n, a Hebron…®n nguibam isa a gan…®ngi. Ez…® an ovavir boriba a gapiagha ikia kamagh…®ra iti.
\v 15 (Fom…®ra, me ziam Kiriat Arba, Hebron…®n nguibam gar…®si. Arba, an Anakian gumazir ruarir bar ekiar mam.)
\p Kalep nguazir kam inigha g…®vaz…®, m…®doroziba uam Kenan…®n nguazir kam…®n otivir puvat…®.
\c 15
\s1 Nguazir Josua Judan anabam bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Judan anabam…®n adarazi bar nguazir me Juda bagha b…®ghizim inigha a gapia. Ez…® Judabar nguazir m…®taghniam saut…®n amadaghan ghua, Idom…®n kantrin tugha, bar ghua Sen…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim sara ghu.
\v 2 Men nguazir m…®taghniar saut…®n amadaghan itim, an Amangs…®zim Itir D…®par Akarem…®n saut…®n itir ruaghatevim…®n ikegha ghua,
\v 3 tuavir Akrabim…®n ghuavanadim gitagha ghua saut…®n amadaghan Sen…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n otogha ghua, Kades Barnea gitagha ghua Hesron…®n nguibam gitagha ghua, Adar…®n nguibam…®n oto. Egha ragh…®r…®gha ghua Karkan nguibam…®n oto.
\v 4 Egha ghua Asmon…®n nguibam…®n otogha, Isip…®n nguazim…®n m…®taghniam ab…®ghizir daghurir muziarim…®n ghuavanaga Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n tu. Kar Judabar nguazir saut…®n amadaghan itim…®n m…®taghniam.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® men nguazir m…®taghniar aruem anadi nagh…®n itim, an Amangs…®zim Itir D…®par Akarem…®n, m…®riam bar an ghuanaga Jordan…®n Fanem…®n akam…®n oto. Ez…® not…®n amadaghan itir nguazir m…®taghniam, a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n akam…®n ikegha,
\v 6 ghua Bethoklan nguibam…®n otogha ghua, not…®n amadaghan ghua Betaraban nguibam…®n otogha ghua Bohan…®n dag…®am…®n oto. (Bohan, a Ruben…®n otarir mam…®n ziam.)
\v 7 Egha Akor…®n danganir zarim…®n ghua, Debir…®n nguibam…®n otogha, not…®n amadaghan ragha ghua Gilgal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. N…® Gilgal…®n nguibam…®n tugh gant…®, tuavir akar Adumim…®n nguibam…®n ghuavanadim iti. A danganir zarir kam…®n saut…®n amadaghan m…®ghs…®abar iti. Egha m…®taghniam ghua Ensemes…®n d…®pam…®n otogha, ghua Enrogel…®n danganim…®n oto.
\v 8 Egha saut…®n amadaghan ghua Hinom…®n Otarim…®n danganir zarim…®n ghua Jebus…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n oto. Jerusalem…®n nguibam danganir kam…®n iti. Ez…® nguazir m…®taghniam ghuav…®ra ikia ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan itir m…®ghs…®am…®n oto, a Hinom…®n danganir zarim…®n m…®riam…®n iti. M…®ghs…®ar kam, a Refaim…®n danganir zarim…®n iti.
\v 9 Egha ghua Neptoan d…®par em…®m…®rim…®n otogha ghua Efron…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n itir nguibabar oto. Egha kagh nguazir m…®taghniam ua ragha ghua Balan nguibam…®n oto, an ziar mam Kiriat Jearim.
\v 10 Egha Balan nguibam…®n m…®taghniam ua ighuigha ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n ghua, Ser…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n otogha ghua, Jearim…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n vong…®n not…®n amadaghan itir danganim…®n oto, an ziar mam Kesalon. Egha ghuaghira Betsemes…®n nguibam…®n otogha ghua Timnan nguibam gita.
\v 11 Egha ghua Ekron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n not…®n amadaghan itir m…®ghs…®am…®n otogha ighuigha ghua Sikeron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha ghua, Balan m…®ghs…®am ategha ghua Japnel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Nguazir kam…®n m…®taghniam ghua Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n g…®fa.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Judan anabam…®n nguazir aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itibar m…®taghniam, a Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam, bar an m…®riamra ghu. Ez…® Judan anabam…®n aven itir ik…®ziba vaghvagha nguazir kaba inigha dagh apiaghav iti.
\s1 Kalep Hebron ko Debir…®n // nguibar ekiamning ini
\r (Gumazir Dapaniba 1:11-15)
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 15:13-14 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 1:20\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, fom…®ra Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, me Judabar nguazim…®n nguazitam is…® Jefunen otarim, Kalep dan…®ngigh. Ez…® Josua Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®n amua, Hebron…®n nguibam isava Kalep gan…®ngi. Hebron…®n ziar mam Kiriat Arba. Arba ana Anakian ovavim.
\v 14 Ez…® Kalep Anakian ik…®zir 3pla m…®sogha, men ag…®nt…®zima me are. Men ziabar kara: Sesai ko Ahiman ko Talmai, me Anak…®n ovavir boriba.
\v 15 Egha g…®n Kalep nguibar kam ategha ghua Debir…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamizibav sosi. (Nguibar kam…®n ziar mam, Kiriat Sefer.)
\p 
\v 16 Egha Kalep kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazim Kiriat Sefer…®n gumazibav sogh me ab…®raght…®, k…® uan guivim Aksa a danight…® an an ikiam.‚Äù
\v 17 Ez…® Kalep…®n dozim Kenas, an otarim Otniel, nguibar kam…®n gumazibav sogha me ab…®ra. Ez…® Kalep uan guivim Aksa isa, a gan…®ngiz…® an an iti.
\v 18 Egha aning uaning…®n ikiava, Aksa Otniel bagha iza aneb…®rava, a m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan afeziam Kalep…®n azaraght…® a nguazitam atugh ga dan…®ngigh. Egha Aksa ghua Kalep batogha uan donkin faghaf…®ragha izaghirima, Kalep an azara, ‚ÄúK…® bizir tizitam n…® bagh a damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Aksa uan afeziam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® bizir aghuitam na dan…®ngigh. N…® faragha d…®paba puvat…®zir nguazim Negev…®n itir nguazir akuar mam abigha na gan…®ngi. Dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® d…®par em…®m…®riba itir nguazir aghuitam abigh na dan…®ngigh.‚Äù Ez…® Kalep d…®par em…®m…®riba itir nguazir pumuning a gan…®ngi. Aning Hebron…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n iti, mam p…®n amadaghan itima, mam v…®n amadaghan iti.
\s1 Judabar nguibabar ziaba
\p 
\v 20 Kar Judan anabam…®n aven itir ik…®ziba inizir nguibaba ko nguaziba.
\v 21 Nguibar saut…®n amadaghan ikia Idom…®n nguazim…®n m…®taghniam…®n borogh…®n itiba, dar ziabar kara: Kapsel, Eder, Jagur,
\v 22 Kina, Dimona, Adada,
\v 23 Kedes, Hasor, Itnan,
\v 24 Sip, Telem, Bealot,
\v 25 Hasor Hadata, Keriot ko Hesron, an ziar mam Hasor,
\v 26 Amam, Sema, Molada,
\v 27 Hasargada, Hesmon, Betpelet,
\v 28 Hasarsual, Berseba, Bisiotia,
\v 29 Bala, Im, Esem,
\v 30 Eltolat, Kesil, Horma,
\v 31 Siklak, Matmana, Sansana,
\v 32 Lebaot, Silhim, Ain, ko Rimon. Distrigh…®n kam, 29plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® distrigh…®n maba aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itir m…®ghs…®ar dozibagh is…®n iti. Ez…® distrigh…®n kabar mam, nguibar ekiar kaba an aven iti: Estaol, Sora, Asna,
\v 34 Sanoa, Enganim, Tapua, Enam,
\v 35 Jarmut, Adulam, Soko, Aseka,
\v 36 Saraim, Aditaim, ko Gedera, an ziar mam, Gederotaim. Distrigh…®n kam 14plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 37 Ez…® distrigh…®n igharazim…®n itir nguibar ekiabar kara: Senan, Hadasa, Mikdalgat,
\v 38 Dilean, Mispa, Joktel,
\v 39 Lakis, Boskat, Eklon,
\v 40 Kabon, Lamas, Kitlis,
\v 41 Gederot, Betdagon, Nama, ko Makeda. Distrigh…®n kam 16plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 42 Ez…® distrigh…®n igharazim…®n itir nguibar ekiabar kara: Lipna, Eter, Asan,
\v 43 Ipta, Asna, Nesip,
\v 44 Keila, Aksip, ko Maresa. Distrigh…®n kam 9plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 45 Ez…® distrigh…®n igharazim…®n itir nguibar ekiabar kara: Ekron…®n nguibam, an nguibar ekiaba, ko an nguibar doziba,
\v 46 nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar dozir Asdot…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n, Ekron…®n ikegha ghua ongarir dadarim…®n tu.
\v 47 Egha ghua Asdot ko Gasan nguibam ko nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar uari inigha itiba, bar dar ghua saut…®n amadaghan Isip…®n Daghurir D…®pam…®n otogha, bar ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n tu.
\p 
\v 48 Egha distrigh…®n maba nguazir m…®ghs…®abar iti. Ez…® danganir kam…®n itir nguibar ekiabar kara: Samir, Jatir, Soko,
\v 49 Dana, Kiriat Sefer, an ziar mam Debir,
\v 50 Anap, Estemoa, Anim,
\v 51 Gosen, Holon, Gilo. Distrigh…®n kam 11plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 52 Ez…® nguibar ekiar distrigh…®n igharazim…®n itibar ziabar kara: Arap, Duma, Esan,
\v 53 Janim, Bet Tapua, Afeka,
\v 54 Humta, Kiriat Arba, an ziar mam, Hebron, ko Sior. Distrigh…®n kam, 9plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 55 Ez…® nguibar ekiar distrigh…®n igharazim…®n itibar ziabar kara: Maon, Karmel, Sif, Juta,
\v 56 Jesril, Jokdeam, Sanoa,
\v 57 Kain, Gibea, ko Timna. Distrigh…®n kam 10plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 58 Ez…® nguibar ekiar distrigh…®n igharazim…®n itibar ziabar kara: Halhul, Betsur, Gedor,
\v 59 Marat, Betanot, ko Eltekon. Distrigh…®n kam 6plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 60 Ez…® nguibar ekiar distrigh…®n igharazim…®n itibar ziabar kara: Kiriat Bal, an ziar mam Kiriat Jearim, ko Raba. Distrigh…®n kam nguibar ekiar pumuning an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba aning…®n borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 61 Nguibar ekiar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itibar kara: Betaraba, Midin, Sekaka,
\v 62 Nipsan, Amangs…®zir Nguibam, ko Engedi. Distrigh…®n kam 6plan nguibar ekiaba an iti, ez…® nguibar dozir maba dar borogh…®n iti.
\p 
\v 63 \x - \xo 15:63 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 1:21; 2 Samuel 5:6; 1 Eghaghaniba 11:4\x*Judaba Jebusia batoghan ibura, kar gumazamizir Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itiba. Kamagh…®n, me Judaba ko bar mogh…®ra uari inigha Jerusalem…®n ikiav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 15:63 \ft Akar kam, ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n ikiav…®ra iti,‚Äù kar en dughiam…®n akam puvat…®. A gumazim ak…®nafarir kam osirizir dughiam…®n m…®gei.\f*
\c 16
\s1 Nguazir me Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® nguazir me Josep…®n ovavir boriba bagha b…®ghizim, an m…®taghniam Jordan…®n Fanem borogh…®n itir nguibam Jerikon ikegha, aruem anadi nagh…®n amadaghan Jerikon mozir pabar ikegha ghua not…®n amadaghan ghua, gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghua, ruarir m…®ghs…®abar ghua Betel…®n nguibam…®n oto.
\v 2 A Betel…®n otogha ghua, Lus…®n nguibam…®n otogha ghua Atarot…®n oto, danganir kam Arkaia an ike.
\v 3 Egha aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan ghua, Japletian danganim…®n ghua, bar ghua v…®n Itir Bethoron…®n nguibam…®n oto. Egha ghua Geser…®n nguibam…®n otogha, bar ghua Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n tu.
\p 
\v 4 Josep…®n ovavir boriba, kar Manasen anabam…®n adarazi ko Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarasi, me nguazir kaba ini.
\p 
\v 5 Kar Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazir nguaziba. Men nguazir m…®taghniam, aruem anadi nagh…®n amadaghan Atarot Adar…®n nguibam…®n ikegha ghua Bethoron nguibam…®n tu.
\v 6 Egha ghua Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n oto. Ez…® Mikmetat…®n nguibam, a not…®n amadaghan ikia men nguazim…®n iti. Ez…® men m…®taghniam aruem anadi nagh…®n amadaghan ighuigha ghua, Tanatsilon nguibam gitagha ghua, aruem anadi nagh…®n amadaghan ghua Janoan nguibar ekiam…®n tu.
\v 7 Egha Janoan nguibam ategha ghua Atarot…®n nguibar ekiam ko Naran nguibar ekiam giraghu. Egha ghua Jerikon nguibar ekiam…®n otogha ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n tu.
\v 8-9 Egha Tapuan nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha ghua, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan ghua, Kanan Fanem…®n otogha ghua Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n tu. Nguazir kam ko nguibar ekiaba, ko nguibar dozir men borogh…®n itiba, me bar ada isa Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazigh an…®ngi. Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazir marasi, men nguibar ekiar maba ko doziba Manasen nguazim…®n aven iti.
\v 10 \x - \xo 16:10 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 1:29\x*Efraim…®n adarasi, Kenanian Geser…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itibav sogha me batoghezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, Kenania Efraimian tong…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® Efraimia, Kenania gamima me pura men ingangarir gumazibar iti.
\c 17
\s1 Nguazir me Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n igharazim bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® nguazir me Josep…®n otarir ivariam Manasen anabam…®n adarazi bagha b…®ghizir nguazim, me an ovavir boribagh an…®ngi. Ez…® Makir, a Manasen otarir ivariam, a Gileat…®n afeziam, a m…®dorozir gumazir bar aghuim. Kamagh…®n me faraghav…®ra Gileat…®n Distrik ko Basan…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguaziba isa an ovavir boribagh an…®ngi.
\v 2 Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan Jordan…®n Fanem…®n itir nguaziba isa, Manasen ovavir borir igharazibagh an…®ngi. Manasen ovavir boribar ziabar kara: Abieser, Helek, Asriel, Sekem, Hefer, Semida. Gumazir kaba, me vaghvagha uan ik…®zir ekiabar inazir afeziabar otifi.
\v 3 Manase, Makir bate, ez…® Makir, Gileat bate, ez…® Gileat Hefer bate, ez…® Hefer Selofehat bate, ez…® Selofehat, a guivibaram ote, egha otariba puvat…®. Ez…® an guivibar ziabar kara: Mala, Noa, Hokla, Milka, ko Tirsa.
\v 4 \x - \xo 17:4 \xt D…®boboniba 27:1-7\x*Ez…® guivir kaba ghua ofa gamir gumazim Eleasar, ko Josua ko gumazir dapanibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòEn afeziam…®n aveghbuabar otariba tong…®n ia nguazitam e dan…®ngigh.‚Äô ‚Äù Ez…® Josua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua, nguaziba ab…®gha Selofehat…®n guivibagh an…®ga, egha magh…®ra Manasen anabam…®n aven itir gumaziba saram an…®ngi.
\v 5-6 Josua nguaziba ab…®gha da isa Manasen anabam…®n adarazir guiviba ko otaribagh an…®ngi. Kamagh…®n Manasen anabam…®n adarasi, bar mogh…®ra 10plan nguaziba bar ada ini. Ez…® Manasen anabam…®n ik…®zir igharazim…®n adarasi, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n amadaghan Gileat…®n Distrik ko Basan…®n Distrigh…®n nguaziba ini.
\p 
\v 7 Manasen anabam…®n adarazir nguazir m…®taghniam, Aser…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n ikegha ghua Mikmetat…®n nguibam…®n oto, an aruem anadi nagh…®n amadaghan Sekem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n iti. Egha m…®taghniam saut…®n amadaghan ghua Entapuabar nguazim…®n tu.
\v 8 Ez…® Manasen anabam…®n nguazim ko Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n m…®taghniam, Tapuan nguibar ekiam…®n kagh iti. Egha Tapuan nguibam uab…®, a Efraimbar nguibam. Ez…® nguazir Tapuan nguibam ek…®aruzim, a Manasen adarazir nguazim.
\v 9-10 Ez…® Efraim…®n adarazir nguibar ekiaba, kar nguibar ekiar saut…®n amadaghan itiba, ez…® Manasen adarazir nguazim not…®n amadaghan iti, ez…® aning…®n nguazir m…®taghniam aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Kanan daghurim…®n uaghira, Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n m…®riam bar an ghu. Ez…® Aser…®n nguazim not ko aruem uaghiri nagh…®n aning…®n tong…®ra iti, ez…® Isakar…®n adarazir nguazim, not ko aruem anadi nagh…®n aning…®n tong…®ra iti.
\v 11 Isakar ko Aser…®n nguazir m…®taghniamning…®n aven, Manasen anabam, nguibar kaba ini: Betsan, ko Ipleam, ko nguibar aning okarigha itiba, Nafat Dor, Endor, Tanak, ko Megido, ko nguibar da okarigha itiba.\f + \fr 17:11 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 12 \x - \xo 17:12-13 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 1:27-28\x*Ez…® Manasen anabam…®n adarasi, Kenan…®n gumazamiziba nguibar ekiar kabar me batoghan ibura, ez…® me me ko nguibar ekiar kabar ikiav…®ra iti.
\v 13 Ez…® Israelia g…®n gavgavim inigha, Kenania ab…®rima, me pura men ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar iti. Egha me me batoghezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 14 Egha g…®n Josep…®n ovavir boriba, Josua bagha izegha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God bar deragha e gamiz…®, e bar av…®raseme. Ez…® e nguazir av…®ritaba inian f…®r…®n, n…® nguazir vam…®ra isava e gan…®ngi.‚Äù
\v 15 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIan av…®rim bar ekeveght…® Efraimbar m…®ghs…®abar itir nguazim ian suvight…®, ia uari ghuanang Peresia ko Refaimian ruarir ghurim…®n mang…®, uari baghv…®ra nguazitam…®n gan…®va anezenegh.‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® Josep…®n ovavir boriba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúM…®ghs…®ar nguazir kam en sufi. Kenania, me danganir zarim…®n nguazir vorogh…®ra ireghav itiba, me bar mogh…®ra m…®dorozir karis…®n ain…®n gavgaviba itiba iti. Betsan…®n nguibar ekiam ko an okarigha itir nguibaba ko, Jesril…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n danganir zarim…®n itir adarasi, me bar ain…®n m…®dorozir karisba iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n Efraim ko Manasen anabamning…®n adarazir n…®ghn…®ziba fa me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIan anabamning…®n aven ia guizbang…®ra bar av…®rasemegha, bar gavgafi. Nguazir vam…®ra, a ian sufi. Kamagh…®n, ia nguazir igharazitaba uaghan ada iniam.
\v 18 Egh nguibar m…®ghs…®abar itiba, ia bar mogh…®ram ada iniam. Ruarir kam a guizbang…®ra ruarir ghurir p…®zim, ia an m…®taghniar tam…®n ikegh an ingar mang…®, an saghon itir m…®taghniar igharazim…®n otogh. Kenania gavgavigha m…®dorozir karis…®n bar gavgaviba iti. Eght…® ia me m…®sogh men ag…®nt…®ght…® me aregham.‚Äù
\c 18
\s1 Josua nguazir igharazim bar aneb…®gha Israelia bar me gan…®di
\p 
\v 1 Egha Israelia m…®dorozim gamigha apaniba ab…®nigha g…®vagha, Silon nguibar ekiam…®n uari akufa. Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fasa a bativamin Purirpenim asara.
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n Israelian tong…®n 7plan anababar adarasi, me uari bagh nguazitaba t…®ghar da iniam.
\v 3 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, ian inazir afeziabar God, nguazir kam ia ganigha g…®fa. Ez…® ia manmagh…®n amigha ghuava a inizir puvat…®?
\v 4 Ia 7plan anabar nguaziba puvat…®zibar gumaziba vaghvagh men aven, 3plan gumazibav sefegh. Eght…® k…® me amadaght…® me nguazim bar a daruva, an gan nguazir me ifongeziba uari bagh ada inis…®, da osirigh, g…®n uamategh na bagh iz…®, osirizir eghaghanir kam na dan…®ngigh.
\v 5 Me nguazim, 7plan akuabar aneb…®kigh. Judan anabam…®n adarazi saut…®n amadaghan nguazim inigha g…®fa, egh me anar…®ra ikiam. Ez…® Josep…®n adarazi not…®n amadaghan nguazim ini, egh me anar…®ra ikiam.
\v 6 Eght…® ia 7plan anababa meng, me bagh nguazim ab…®gh…®va, dar eghaghaniba osirigh, eghaghanir kaba inigh iz…® na dan…®ngigh. Eght…® k…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n damazim…®n nguazir me ifuegh iniamim g…®fofoghs…®, satu gikiararangam.
\v 7 Eght…® bizir gumaziba inigha iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damuasa avim…®n tueba, kar Livain anabam…®n adarazi damuamin ingangarim. Ez…® kamagh…®n, Josua nguazitam isava Livain adarazigh an…®ngizir puvat…®. Ez…® Gat…®n anabam, Ruben…®n anabam, ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n nguaziba inigha g…®fa. Nguazir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, me gan…®ngizir nguaziba.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n gumazir mangasa m…®sevezibav gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® nguazim ab…®gh…®rarigh an eghaghaniba na bagh bar ada osirigh da inigh iz…®t…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n satu gikararang fogh suam, nguazir manam God ia bagh a ginaba.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kaba Josuan m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha ghue.
\v 9 Me ghua nguazir kaba bar dagh etiagha aruigha, nguazibar aven nguibar ekiabar ziaba vaghvagha da osirigha, 7plan akuabar da abigha dar eghaghaniba osiri. Egha me g…®n uamategha Josua bagha Silon ize.
\v 10 Ez…® Josua Silon ikia fofoghasa, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n satu gikararai, eght…®, a manmagh…®ra nguaziba abigh vaghvagh men 7plan anababar an…®ngam. Egha a g…®n nguazir kaba abigha Israelian anababa vaghvagha me gan…®di.
\s1 Nguazir me Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 11 Dughiar kam Josua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n satu gikararaima, Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi iniamin nguazim faragha oto. Nguazir kam, Judan anabam…®n adarazi ko Josep…®n anabam…®n adarazigh an…®ngizir nguazimning…®n tong…®ra iti.
\v 12 Men not…®n amadaghan itir nguazir m…®taghniam, a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n ikegha ghua, Jerikon nguibar ekiar m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n itim…®n m…®riam…®n not…®n amadaghan ghua a gitagha ghu. Egha kagh ighuigha ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n, bar ghua Betaven…®n nguazir m…®s…®ngizim…®n danganim…®n oto.
