\v 18 Isakar…®n anabam…®n nguazim, an aven nguibar ekiabar ziabar kara: Jesril, Kesulot, Sunem,
\v 19 ko Hafaraim, Sion, Anaharat,
\v 20 ko Rabit, Kision, Ebes,
\v 21 ko Remet, Enganim, Enhada, ko Betpases.
\v 22-23 Isakar…®n anabam…®n nguazir m…®taghniam ghua, Tabor…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n suiragha ghua Sahasuman nguibar ekiam…®n otogha, ghua Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n oto. Isakar…®n anabam…®n adarasi, nguibar ekiar 16pla, ko nguibar dozir dar borogh…®n itiba ini.
\s1 Nguazir me Aser…®n anabam…®n adarazi bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 24 Josua ghua satu gikararaima, Isakar…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n g…®n, nguazir namba 5 Aser…®n anabam…®n adarazi bagha otoz…®, me me bagha aneb…®ki.
\v 25 Aser…®n anabam inizir nguazim…®n aven itir nguibar ekiabar ziabar kara: Helkat, Hali, Beten, Aksap,
\v 26 ko Alamelek, Amat, ko Misal. Ez…® aruem uaghiri nagh…®n men m…®taghniam Karmel…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n ghua Sihorlipnat…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu.
\v 27 Egha ighuigha ghua aruem anadi nagh…®n ghua, Betdagon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha, Sebulun…®n adarazir nguazim…®n borogh…®ra ghua, Iptahel…®n danganir zarim…®n ghua not…®n amadaghan Betemek ko Neiel…®n nguibamning…®n tu. Egha m…®taghniam ghuav…®ra ikia ghua, not…®n amadaghan ghua Kabul…®n nguibam…®n otogha,
\v 28 ghua Ebron, Rehop, Hamon, ko Kanan otogha, bar ghua Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu.
\v 29 Egha ua ighuigha Raman nguibar ekiam…®n otogha iza, Tair…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu, nguibar ekiar kam…®n d…®vazim bar gavgafi. Egha m…®taghniam ua ragha Hosan nguibar ekiam…®n otogha ghua Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n tu. Aser…®n anabam uaghan nguibar ekiar kaba ini: Mehebel, Aksip,
\v 30-31 ko Uma, Afek, ko Rehop. Aser…®n anabam…®n adarasi, nguibar ekiar 22pla, ko nguibar dozir dar borogh…®n itiba ini.
\s1 Nguazir me Naptalin anabam…®n adarazi bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 32 Josua ghua satu gikararaima, Aser…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n g…®n, nguazir namba 6 Naptalin anabam…®n adarazi bagha otoz…®, me me bagha aneb…®ki.
\v 33 Ez…® men nguazir m…®taghniam, Helep…®n nguibar ekiam ko Sananim…®n nguibam…®n tughav itir Ok…®n temer ekiam…®n povim…®n ikegha ghua, Adami Nekep…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha ghua, Japnel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha, ghua Lakum…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n oto.
\v 34 Egha m…®taghniam ighuigha aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan ghua Asnot Tabor…®n nguibar ekiam ko Hukok…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Ez…® Sebulun…®n anabam…®n nguazir m…®taghniar saut…®n itim, a Naptalin anabam…®n nguazir m…®taghniam…®n suira. Ez…® Naptalin nguazir m…®taghniar aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itim, an Aser…®n anabam…®n nguazir m…®taghniam…®n suira. Egha an nguazir m…®taghniar aruem anadi nagh…®n itim, a Jehudan nguibam…®n borogh…®n ikia Jordan…®n Fanem…®n suira.\f + \fr 19:34 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 35 Men nguibar ekiar d…®vazir gavgaviba itiba, dar ziabar kara: Sidim, Ser, Hamat, Rakat, Kineret,
\v 36 ko Adama, Rama, Hasor,
\v 37 ko Kedes, Edrei, Enhasor,
\v 38-39 ko Yiron, Mikdalel, Horem, Betanat, ko Betsemes. Naptalin anabam, 19plan nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar dozir dar borogh…®n itiba ini.
\s1 Nguazir me Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 40 Josua ghua satu gikararaima, Naptalin anabam…®n nguazim…®n g…®n, nguazir namba 7 Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi bagha otoz…®, me me bagha aneb…®ki.
\v 41 Dan…®n anabam inizir nguazim, an nguibar ekiabar ziabar kara: Sora, Estaol, Irsemes,
\v 42 ko Salbim, Aijalon, Itla,
\v 43 ko Elon, Timna, Ekron,
\v 44 ko Elteken, Gibeton, Balat,
\v 45 ko Jehut, Beneberak, Gatrimon,
\v 46 ko Mejarkon, Rakon, ko Jopan nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n itir danganim.
\v 47 \x - \xo 19:47 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 18:27-29\x*Ez…® g…®n, nguazir kam…®n ghuavir faraghav itiba, Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazir apanim gamigha nguazir kam…®n me batoke. Ez…® Dan…®n adarazi d…®kavigha ghua Lais…®n nguibam…®n otogha, me m…®sogha nguibar ekiar kam…®n gumazamiziba bar me m…®suagharigha men nguibar ekiam ini. Egha Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi ghaze, nguazir kam mena, egha a gaperagha an iti. Me ziar kam Lais adegha uan inazir afeziam…®n ziam Dan a gat…®.
\v 48 Nguibar ekiar kaba, ko nguibar dozir dar borogh…®n itiba, Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi da ini.
\s1 Nguazir me Josuan adarazi bagha b…®ghizim
\p 
\v 49 Israelia bar nguaziba ab…®gha uari ganigha g…®vagha, nguazir mam isa Nun…®n otarim Josuan adarazigh an…®ngi.
\v 50 Josua faragha Timnat Seran nguibar ekiam uab…® dan…®ngasa men azai, an Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n ikia m…®ghs…®aba itir danganim…®n iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, me a isava a gan…®ngi. Ez…® Josua nguibar kam uam an ingarigha, a gaperaghav an iti.
\p 
\v 51 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim Eleasar ko, Josua ko Israelian anababar ik…®ziba vaghvagha men gumazir dapaniba ko Silon danganim…®n, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ikia, egha God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n apiaghav iti. Egha Israelian anababa bagha inabazir nguaziba ab…®ghasa satu gikararai. Ez…® me nguaziba tuiragha uari gan…®dir ingangarir kam, ghua kamagh…®ra tugha g…®fa.
\c 20
\s1 Josua nguibar ekiar gumazamiziba ar…® mang…® mongamiba am…®sefe
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 20:1-9 \xt D…®boboniba 35:6-32; God…®n Araziba 4:41-43; 19:1-13\x*Ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God Josua m…®g…®a ghaze,
\v 2 ‚ÄúK…® faragha Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra n…® Israelia m…®k…®mt…®, me nguibar ekiar gumazamiziba ar…® mang…® mongamibagh, inamight…® da ik…®.
\v 3 Eght…® ian gumazitam, atamakuigh gumazitam m…®sueght…® an aremegham, an ar…® mang…® nguibar ekiar kabar tam…®n modogh ikiam. Eght…® aremezir gumazim…®n tav uam a ikarvaghs…® a burian kogham.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir os…®mt…®zim gamizim nguibar ekiar kam…®n mongs…® mang…® otogh, faragh mang…® nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n, uan os…®mt…®zim…®n gun gumazir aruabav kemegh. Eght…® me an amamangat…®ght…®, a mang…® me ko ikiam.
\v 5 Eght…® gumazir a ikarvaghasava amim an g…®n iz…®t…®, nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir dapaniba a is…® an agharim dat…®ghan kogham. Me fo, a guizbang…®ra an apanim gamua a m…®soghez…® ana aremezir puvat…®. Egh nguibar ekiar kam…®n gumazamiziba a geghuv deragh an ganam.
\v 6 Egh a nguibar ekiar kam…®n averara ik…® mang…®t…®, me gumazamizibar damazim…®n kot…®n aven, an os…®mt…®zim tuis…®gh a bareght…®, an kot deraght…®, a nguibar ekiar kam…®n averara ik…® mang…®t…®, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim ovengeghamin dughiam otogham. Eght…® g…®n a uamategh uan nguibar a ikegha ara izezim…®n mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® me kamagh…®n oregha Naptalin anabam…®n nguibar m…®ghs…®am…®n itir mam Kedes ginaba. A Galilin Distrigh…®n aven iti. Egha Efraim…®n nguibar m…®ghs…®am…®n itim, Sekem ginaba. Egha Kiriat Arba, an ziar mam Hebron, me a ginaba. A Judan anabam…®n nguibar m…®ghs…®am…®n itim.
\v 8 Egha me Ruben…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n, Beser…®n nguibam ginaba. N…® Jerikon tugh Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n gant…®, Beser…®n nguibar m…®ghs…®am ikiam. An aruem anadi nagh…®n d…®paba puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti. Egha Gat…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n, Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n aven, me Ramot…®n nguibar ekiam ginaba. Egha Manasen anabam…®n nguazim…®n, Basan…®n Distrigh…®n aven, Golan…®n nguibar ekiam ginaba.
\v 9 Nguibar ekiar mongamin kaba, kar Israelia, ko Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir me ko itiba, me me bagha dagh inaba, eght…® men tav atamakuigh gumazitam m…®soght…® an aremeght…®, an tav a ikarvaghs…® damut…®, an atiating ivegh mang…® nguibar ekiar kabar aven mang…® deragh ikiam. A kagh ik…® mang…®t…® kotiar dughiam…®n gumazamiziba bar a baregham. Eght…® gumazir ovevem ikaraghasa amim, faragh deraghv…®ra oregh fogh suam, gumazir kam ti guizbang…®ra n…®ghnigha a m…®soghez…® an areme, o puvat…®. Kot m…®k…®m suam, Gumazir kam os…®mt…®zim guizbang…®ra iti, eght…® an a ikaragham. Puvat…®ght…®, puvat…®gham.
\c 21
\s1 Nguibar ekiar me Livain anabam…®n adarazigh an…®ngiziba
\p 
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 21:1-2 \xt D…®boboniba 35:1-8\x*Israelia dughiar kam…®n Kenan…®n nguazim…®n, Silon nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n nguibam aghuigha an iti. Ez…® Livain anabam…®n gumazir dapaniba ghua, ofa gamir gumazim, Eleasar ko Josua ko Israelian anababar gumazir dapaniba me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® Livain anabam…®n adarasi, nguibar ekiar danganir aghuiba iti taba ko dar borogh…®n itir nguazir men as…®ziba ikiamiba, da is…® me dan…®ng.‚Äù
\v 3 Ez…® Israelian anababa, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, amua vaghvagha uan nguibar ekiar maba ko men as…®ziba ikiamin nguazir maba isava Livain anabam…®n adarazigh an…®ngi.
\p 
\v 4 Me faraghav…®ra Kohat…®n adarazi iniamin nguibar ekiaba bagha satu gikararai. Kohat…®n ik…®zir igharazim, men inazir afeziam Aron, an ofa gamir gumazim. Ez…® Judan anabam ko Simeon…®n anabam, ko Benjamin…®n anabam, me 13plan nguibar ekiaba atugha me gan…®ngi.
\v 5 Ez…® Kohat…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazamizir igharaziba, Efraim…®n anabam ko Dan…®n anabam, ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n ik…®zir aruem uaghiri nagh…®n amadaghan itim, me uan nguibar ekiar 10pla atugha me gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Gerson…®n ik…®zim…®n adarasi, Isakar…®n anabam, ko Aser…®n anabam, Naptalin anabam, ko Manasen anabar ik…®zir aruem anadi nagh…®n itim, me uan nguibar ekiar 13pla atugha me gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Merarin ik…®zim…®n adarasi, Ruben…®n anabam, ko Gat…®n anabam, ko Sebulun…®n anabam, me uan 12plan nguibar ekiaba atugha me gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 8 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, me Livain anabam…®n adarazi bagha nguibar ekiar danganir aghuiba iti taba me dan…®ngasa satu gikararai. Eght…® nguibar ekiar kabar borogh…®n itir nguaziba, Livain adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®ght…® da ikiam.
\p 
\v 9-10 Kar Judan anabam ko Simeon…®n anabam, me gan…®ngizir nguibar ekiaba. Israelia nguibar ekiar kaba me dan…®ngasa satu gikararangiz…®, Aron…®n ovavir boriba Kohat…®n ik…®zim…®n aven itir adarasi, da ini.
\v 11 Israelia, Kiriat Arban nguibar ekiam isa Aron…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, nguibar kam, an ziar mam Hebron. Ez…® Arba a Anak…®n afeziam. Hebron…®n nguibar ekiam, a Judan anabam…®n nguazim…®n aven ikia, egha m…®ghs…®abagh is…®n iti, ez…® nguazir av…®riba an okarigha iti. Eght…® me uan as…®ziba nguazir kabar dar ar…®gham.
\v 12 Nguibar ekiar kam…®n, Israelia faragha azeniba oparamin nguazir an borogh…®n itiba, ko an nguibar dozir an borogh…®n itiba, me da isa Jefunen otarim Kalep ganigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n, me dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazir kaba ko nguibar doziba is…® Aron…®n adarazir an…®ngan kogham.
\p 
\v 13 Hebron, a nguibar ekiar gumaziba ar…® mang…® mongamin mam. Egha me uaghan nguibar ekiar igharaziba isa Aron…®n ovavir boribagh an…®ngi. Dar ziabar kara: Lipna,
\v 14 ko Jatir, Estemoa,
\v 15 ko Holon, Debir,
\v 16 ko Ain, Juta, ko Betsemes. Kar Judan anabam ko Simeon…®n anabam 9plan nguibar ekiaba me gan…®ngi. Eght…® nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itir nguaziba, Livain adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 17 Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi nguibar ekiar 4pla isa me gan…®ngi. Dar ziabar kara: Gibeon, Geba,
\v 18 ko Anatot, Almon. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Livain adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 19 Aron…®n ovavir boriba, me ofa gamir gumaziba, me nguibar ekiar 13pla ini. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, me uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 20 Ez…® Kohat…®n ik…®zir igharaziba, Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi uan nguibar ekiaba me gan…®ngi.
\v 21 Me an…®ngizir nguibar ekiar 4plan kabar ziabar kara: Sekem, a Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazir m…®ghs…®aba itim…®n iti, egha a nguibar ekiar gumaziba ar…® mang…® mongamin mam. A ko Geser…®n nguibar ekiam,
\v 22 ko Kipsaim, Bethoron. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Kohat…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 23 Ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi me nguibar ekiar 4plan kaba isa Kohat…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, dar ziabar kara: Elteken, Gibeton,
\v 24 ko Aijalon, ko Gatrimon. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Kohat…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 25 Egha Manasen anabam me tuirazimning…®n igharazim…®n adarasi, me nguibar ekiar pumuning isa Kohat…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, dar ziabar kara: Tanak ko Gatrimon. Ez…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kamning okarigha itiba, Kohat…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 26 Kamagh…®n, Kohat…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazi bar nguibar ekiar 12pla ko, dar nguazir as…®zibar ar…®ghamiba, ini.
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Gerson…®n ik…®zim, me Livain anabam…®n ik…®zir mam, Israelia nguibar ekiar maba me gan…®ngi. Me Manasen anabam me tuirazimning…®n ik…®zir faragha zuim…®n nguibar ekiar pumuning isa Gerson…®n adarazigh an…®ngi. Aning…®n ziamning kara: Besteran ko Golan, aning Basan…®n Distrigh…®n amadaghan itir nguibar ekiamning. Golan a nguibar ekiar gumaziba ar…® mang…® mongamin mam. A ko Besteran nguibar ekiam. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kamning okarigha itiba, Gerson…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® me Isakar…®n anabam…®n nguibar ekiar 4pla isa Gerson…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, dar ziabar kara: Kision, Daberat,
\v 29 Jarmut, ko Enganim. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Gerson…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 30 Ez…® me Aser…®n anabam…®n adarazir nguibar ekiar 4pla isava Gerson…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, dar ziabar kara: Misal, Apdon,
\v 31 ko Helkat, Rehop. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Gerson…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 32 Egha me Naptalin anabam…®n nguibar ekiar 3pla isa Gerson…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, dar ziabar kara: Kedes, Hamotdor ko Kartan, da Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibar ekiaba, ez…® Kedes, a nguibar ekiar gumaziba ar…® mang…® mongamin mam. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Gerson…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 33 Egha Gerson…®n ik…®zim nguibar ekiar 13pla ini. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, me uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\p 
\v 34 Egha me Sebulun…®n anabam…®n nguibar ekiar 4plan kaba isa Merarin ik…®zim…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, men ik…®zim, Livain anabam…®n gumazamizir igharaziba. Kar 4plan nguibar ekiar kabar ziaba: Jokneam, Karta,
\v 35 ko Dimna, Nahalal. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Merarin adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 36 Ez…® me Ruben…®n anabam…®n nguibar ekiar 4pla isa, Merarin ik…®zim…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, dar ziabar kara: Beser, Jahas,
\v 37 ko Kedemot ko Mefat. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Merarin adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 38 Ez…® me Gat…®n anabam…®n nguibar ekiar 4plan kaba isa Merarin adarazigh an…®ngi, dar ziabar kara: Ramot, a Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguibar ekiam, egha a nguibar ekiar gumaziba ar…® mang…® mongamin mam. Gumaziba os…®mt…®ziba ikia ara ghua an aven modi. A ko Mahanaim,
\v 39 ko Hesbon, ko Jaser. Eght…® nguazir nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Merarin adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\v 40 Kamagh…®n Merarin ik…®zim…®n adarazi nguibar ekiar 12pla bar da ini. Men ik…®zim, Livain anabam…®n gumazamizir igharaziba.
\p 
\v 41 Israelia bar mogh…®ra nguazir me apiazibar tong…®n, 48pla nguibar ekiaba isa Livain anabam…®n adarazigh an…®ngi.
\v 42 Eght…® nguazir bar nguibar ekiar kaba okarigha itiba, Livain anabam…®n adarazi uan as…®zibar ar…®gham.
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®n Israelia bar nguaziba ini
\p 
\v 43 Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra men inazir afeziabav kemez…® mogh…®n, a nguaziba isa, bar Israelia gan…®ngiz…®, me dagh apia.
\v 44 \x - \xo 21:44 \xt God…®n Araziba 7:24; Josua 11:23; 22:4\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim g…®n…®ghn…®gha Israelian akuraz…®, me uan apanibav sogha bar me ab…®niz…®, men apanitam me ab…®razir puvat…®.
\v 45 \x - \xo 21:45 \xt Josua 23:14\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, fom…®ra akar d…®k…®r…®ziba Israelia gan…®ngi, egha a derav…®ra dagh amiz…®, da guizbang…®ram otifi.
\c 22
\s1 Josua, anabar Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n ikiamiba, amadaz…®, me uan nguazibar zui
\p 
\v 1 Israelia, Kenan…®n nguaziba bar da abigha g…®vaz…®, Josua, Ruben…®n anabam ko, Gat…®n anabam, ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam…®n adarasi, a bar men diaz…®, me iza uari akufa.
\v 2 \x - \xo 22:2 \xt D…®boboniba 32:20-32; Josua 1:12-15\x*Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMoses a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim, bizir a damuasa ia m…®geiba ia zurara dagh ami. Egha uaghan, bizir k…® ia damuasa ia m…®geiba, ia uaghan dagh ami.
\v 3 Fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, ia zurara uan aveghbuabar akurvasi. Ia dughiatam…®n me ataghizir puvat…®. Ia bar derav…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zui.
\v 4 Ia fo, Ikiav…®ra God, ian God, uan akar faragha d…®k…®r…®zim…®n g…®n ghua avughsazim ian aveghbuabagh an…®ngi. Kamagh…®n, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n uamategh nguazir ia inizibar mang…® dar apiagh ik…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n itir nguazir kaba ia gan…®ngiz…®, da ian nguazibara.
\v 5 Egh ia Moses damuasa m…®kemezir Akar Gavgaviba ko Moses Osirizir Araziba, ia bar deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mang…® da bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Da ghaze, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, bar a gifongegh, deraghv…®ra an g…®n mang…® an Akar Gavgaviba bar dar amu. Ia zurara pamtem…®n an suiragh. Egh ia uan ifongiaba ko navir averiaba sara, an ingangarim damu.‚Äù
\v 6 Egha Josua God deragh me damuasa God ko m…®kemegha, me amadaz…®, me uan nguibabar zui.
\p 
\v 7 (Moses fom…®ra Basan…®n Distrigh…®n aven itir nguazim isa Manasen anabam…®n akuar mam…®n adarazigh an…®ngi, a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n iti. Ez…® Josua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Jordan…®n Fanem…®n nguazir maba isa Manasen anabam…®n akuar igharazim gan…®ngi.) Egha Josua me m…®geima, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n mangamin gumazamiziba uamategh uan nguibabar mangasava amima, Josua, God deragh me damuasa God…®n azaragha,
\v 8 kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bizir bar av…®riba inigha, da sara zui. As…®ziba, silva, gol, ain, bras, ko korotiar bar aghuiba ia da inigha zui. Ia uan apaniba ab…®ragha inizir bizir kaba, ia da inigh mang…® uan adarazi ko da tuiragh uari dan…®ng.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Ruben…®n anabam, ko Gat…®n anabam ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam, men adarazi uamategha ghua, Israelian igharaziba ataghiz…®, me Kenan…®n nguazim…®n itir nguibam Silon iti. Ez…® me Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguaziba bagha zui. Men nguaziba, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n iti. Fom…®ra Moses me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNguazir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia danight…® ia dar ghuaviba ikegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Egha me bar tuavim…®n ghua Kenan…®n nguazim an ghuav…®ra ikia, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n otogha, ofa gamir dakozir ekiar mam faner m…®riam…®n an ingari.
\v 11 Ez…® Israelian gumazamizir igharaziba bar kamagh…®n oraki, ‚ÄúRuben…®n anabam, Gat…®n anabam ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam, me en amadaghan Jordan…®n Faner m…®riam…®n ofa gamir dakozir mam…®n ingarigha g…®fa.‚Äù
\v 12 Egha Israelia bar mogh…®ra Silon nguibam…®n uari akuvagh, mang…® me ko m…®soghasa n…®ghn…®si.
\p 
\v 13 Egha Israelia, ofa gamir gumazim Eleasar…®n otarim Finias amadaz…®, a Ruben…®n anabam ko Gat…®n anabam, ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam…®n adarazir, ganasa Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n zui.
\v 14 Egha me uan anababar 10pla vaghvagha men tong…®n gumazir dapanir maba am…®sefe. Gumazir dapanir 10plan kaba, me vaghvagha uan ik…®zibar dapaniba. Ez…® Israelia Finias ko gumazir dapanir kaba amangiz…® me a ko zui.
\v 15 Egha me ghua Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n otivigha kamagh…®n Ruben…®n anabam ko Gat…®n anabam ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam batogha kamagh…®n me m…®gei,
\v 16 \x - \xo 22:16 \xt God…®n Araziba 12:13-14\x*‚ÄúE Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamiziba bar, kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ‚ÄòIa manmaghsua God…®n akam batuegha ak…®rim ragha a gasaragha ofa gamir dakozir kam uari baghav…®ram an ingari? Ia ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God ategha an g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 17 \x - \xo 22:17 \xt D…®boboniba 25:1-9\x*Ia fo, e fom…®ra Peor…®n danganim…®n ikia arazir kuram gamiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ar…®mariam amadaz…® a izegha, e an gumazamiziba bar e gas…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® an os…®mt…®zim ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® ia ti ghaze, a pura bizim, egha a gis…®n ua tam damuasa?
\v 18 Egh ia dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n g…®n mangan aghuagh ak…®rim ragh a gasaraght…®, a gurum m…®zaraghan Israelia, bar en ataram.
\v 19 Ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, nguazir ia itim, a God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®, ia anetegh iz…®va Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim itir nguazim…®n izegh an ik…®. Egh en tong…®n uari bagh nguazitaba inigh dar ik…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, an ofa gamir dakozim en tong…®n iti. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam ko en akam baraghan kogh uari bagh ofa gamir dakozir igharazim…®n ingarigh, e damight…®, e ian arazir kuram…®n aven ikian kogham.
\v 20 \x - \xo 22:20 \xt Josua 7:1-26\x*Ia bizir Seran otarim Akan amizim bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®! Ikiav…®ra Itir God e m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Jerikon nguibar ekiam bar a gas…®ghas…®kigh.‚Äù Ez…® Akan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavim batoke. Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God os…®mt…®zir ekiam isa, bar mogh…®ra e gan…®ngi. Akan uan arazir kuram bagha areme, ez…® Israelian igharaziba uaghan an amizir arazir kurar kam bang…®n me ariaghire.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Ruben…®n anabam ko Gat…®n anabam ko Manasen anabar me tuirazimning…®n mam…®n adarasi, Israelian gumazir dapaniba ikaragha ghaze,
\v 22 ‚ÄúGod…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, a guizbang…®ra God. A Ikiav…®ra Itir God. A fo, e bizir kam gami. Ez…® e kamagh…®n ifonge, ia Israelia uaghan bizir kam g…®fogh. E ti uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batueght…®, ia e m…®sueght…® e ar…®m…®ghireght…®, deragham.
\v 23 E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batuegh, uari baghv…®ra ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingarigh, as…®ziba tue da bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofaba, ko wit…®n ofan guar igharazi taba, ko God ko navir vam…®ra ikiasava amir ofaba dar amut…®, kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® e gas…®ghasigham.
\v 24 Bar puvat…®. E ingarizir ofan dakozir kam…®n n…®ghn…®zim kamak…®n, e uan ovavir borir g…®n otivamibagh n…®ghn…®si. E kamagh…®n atiati, ian ovavir boriba ti g…®n, en ovavir boribar anogoregh me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa manmaghsua God…®n ziam fe? A Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e Israelia en God. A ti ian God puvat…®.‚Äô
\v 25 Egh me ti kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, e bagha m…®taghniam at…®, Jordan…®n Fanem Ruben…®n anabam ko Gat…®n anabam, en t…®zim ab…®ki. Ez…® ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n adarazi puvat…®.‚Äô Eght…® ian ovavir boriba en ovavir boribar anogoreght…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fan kogham.
\v 26 Kamagh…®n, e ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n ingariz…®, a tu. E as…®ziba tue da bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofaba ko ofan guar igharaziba bagha an ingarir pu.
\p 
\v 27 ‚ÄúBar puvat…®. E ingarizir ofa gamir dakozir kam, kamagh…®n n…®n ovavir boriba ko en ovavir borir g…®n izamiba, an ababanim…®n m…®n ik…®, kamagh…®n men akakagh suam, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God an Purirpenim…®n mang…® an ziam fam. Egh e uan ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riziba ko, God ko navir vam…®ra ikiasava amir ofaba, ko an ziam fer ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramin igharazibar amuam. Eght…® ian ovavir boriba g…®n kamagh…®n en ovavir boribav k…®man kogh suam, ‚ÄòIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n adarazi puvat…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúEn n…®ghn…®zim kamagh…®n iti, ian ovavir boriba, en ovavir boribav k…®mt…®, me kamagh…®n me ikarvagham, ‚ÄòIa gan, en afeziaba ingarizir ofa gamir dakozim, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n anam ko magh gari. Egha kar, ofan tuer bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko ofan igharazibar amuamin ofa gamir dakozim puvat…®. Dakozir kam an ababanim…®n m…®n iti, ababanir kam kamagh…®n en adarazi ko ian adarazir akakagh suam, ia ko e God…®n vam…®ra iti.‚Äô
\p 
\v 29 ‚ÄúE fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir dakozim, a God…®n damazim…®n ikia an Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n tughav iti. E an ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n danganim inis…®, guiz…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingaran kogham, egh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko wit…®n ofa ko ofan igharazibar amuamin ofabar amuan kogham. E kamagh…®n damigham, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batuegh ak…®rim ragh a gasaragham. E kamagh…®n damuan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim Finias ko Israelian anababa vaghvagha men gumazir dapaniba, me Ruben…®n anabam, ko Gat…®n anabam ko Manasen anabam…®n akuam…®n adarazir, m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha bar akonge.
\v 31 Egha ofa gamir gumazim Eleasar an otarim, Finias, kamagh…®n Ruben…®n anabam ko, Gat…®n anabam ko Manasen anabam…®n akuam, men adaraziv gei, ‚ÄúE dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batoghezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, a uan gumazamiziba ko iti. Egh a dat…®r…®gh…®n en atar…®va, e gas…®ghasighan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Egha g…®n, ofa gamir gumazim Eleasar…®n otarim Finias, ko Israelian gumazir dapaniba, me Ruben…®n anabam ko Gat…®n anabam, Gileat…®n nguibam ategha uamategha Kenan…®n kantrin ghuegha, bizir otivizir kabar gun bar Israelia geghani.
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® Israelia Finias ko gumazir dapaniba m…®kemezir biziba baregha bar akongegha ghaze, ‚ÄúE Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam.‚Äù Egha Ruben ko Gat…®n anabamning…®n adaraziv soghamin n…®ghn…®zir kam, me anetaki.
\p 
\v 34 Kamagh…®n, Ruben ko Gat…®n anabamning…®n adarasi, dakozir kam ziar kam a gat…®, Derav…®ra Gun M…®geir Ofa Gamir Dakozim. An m…®ngarim kamak…®n, ‚ÄúBizir kam, ia ko e an gan fogham, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a uab…®ra God.‚Äù
\c 23
\ms1 Josua areme
\mr (Sapta 23--24)
\s1 Josua akar abuananabar Israelia m…®gei
\p 
\v 1 Azenir av…®riba zuima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God dughiar aghuim isava Israelia gan…®ngiz…®, me avughsa deragha ikiava, uan apaniba ko m…®sozir puvat…®. Ez…® bar g…®n Josua ghua bar ghuri.
\v 2 Egha Josua, Israelia ko men gumazir aruaba ko gumazir dapaniba, ko jasba, ko gumazir gavman…®n faragha zuiba, a bar mogh…®ra me akuvagha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ghurigha g…®fa.
\v 3 Ia uari uan damazibar bizibar ganigha g…®vagha fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian akuragha bizir av…®ribagh amua, ian apanibav sogha me ab…®ni. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian Godra, ia bagha m…®dorozir kam gami.
\v 4 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n derav…®ram oragh, ian nguazim, aruem anadi nagh…®n Jordan…®n Fanem…®n ikegha ghua, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Mediterenian…®n Ongarir Ekiam…®n tu. K…®, apanibav sogha me gafiragha men nguaziba isa ia gan…®ngi. Egha uaghan, nguazir maba, ia t…®ghar apanibav sogh me ab…®nigh, men nguaziba iniam, k…® ia da iniasa k…® dagh inabagha g…®fa.
\v 5 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ian faragh mang…® apanibar amight…® me aregham. A me batueght…® ia pura mang…® nguaziba iniam. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, ia men nguazim inigham.
\v 6 Kamagh…®n, ia bar pamten Moses Osirizir Arazibar Ak…®nafarim…®n aven deraghv…®ra akabar g…®n mang…®. Ia akatam atagh…®raghan mark…®, ia bar mogh…®ra dar suiragh.
\v 7 Egh ia ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ia ko ikiav…®ra itiba, ia me ko poghan mark…®. Ia igharaghv…®ra ik…®. Egh men asebar ziaba d…®ponan mark…®. Ia guizbang…®ra m…®k…®ms…®, aser kabar ziaba d…®ponan mark…®. Egh uaghan teviba ap…®r dar ziaba fan mark…®.
\v 8 Kamagh…®n dera, ia fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n bar derav…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko porogh an g…®n mang…®.
\v 9 Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ik…®zir ekiar, gavgavir ekiaba itiba, an ada batoghez…®, ia puram aven ghua men nguaziba inigha g…®fa. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia adughadughamin gumazitam ua itir puvat…®.
\v 10 \x - \xo 23:10 \xt God…®n Araziba 3:22; 32:30\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, fom…®ra akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, ia bagha apanibav sosi. Egh a ian tav…®n akuraght…®, a 1,000plan gumazibav sogh men ag…®raght…® me aregham.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n, ia bar derav…®ra uari bagh gan. Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, bar a gifongegh.
\v 12 Egh ia ak…®rim ragh God gasaragh, uamategh mang…®, kantrin kam…®n ikiav…®ra itir gumazamiziba ko porogh, me ko poroghamibar amu,
\v 13 egh ia kamagh…®n fogh, God ik…®zir kaba me batueghan kogham. Eght…® me azuaziba as…®zibar suizi mogh…®n, ia bagh azuaziba guight…® da ian suigham. Egh ian ak…®raghariba ifozoroght…®, ia m…®zaziba baraght…®, me d…®konibar ian damazibagh iniv…®ghasam. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia gan…®ngizir nguazir aghuir kam, ia an ik…® m…®zazir kaba ini mang…® g…®n ia ovengam.
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n k…® ia atagh…®raghamin dughiam a rogh…®ra ize. Ez…® ia guizbang…®ra uan navir averiaba ko duabar aven bar fogha g…®fa, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia dan…®ngasa akam ak…®righa g…®vazir bizitam, pura mang…®ghan kogham. A ia ko akam ak…®rizir biziba da guizbang…®ra bar otifi. An akar d…®k…®r…®zir katam pura ghuzir puvat…®.
\v 15 Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir aghuibar g…®n ghuz…® da otiviz…® mogh…®n, a uaghan gant…®, ia an akam batueght…® a ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ivezir kuram ia dan…®ng mang…®, nguazir aghuir a ia ganizir kam…®n aven ia gas…®ghasigham.
\v 16 Ia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a ia ko amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam, ia an g…®n mangan kogh, mang…® asebar ziaba f…®va, aseba bagh teviba ap…®r…®va dar ziaba f…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n an…®ngagharim avim…®n m…®n ian isigham. Eght…® ia dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir aghuir a ia gan…®ngizir kam…®n ikeghan kogham. Ia bar mogh…®ra ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\c 24
\s1 Josuan akar abuananaba
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Josua Sekem…®n nguibam…®n Israelian anababa bar, me akufa. Egha men gumazir aruaba, ko gumazir dapaniba, ko jasba, ko gavman…®n ingangaribar faragha zuir gumaziba, a me inigha God…®n damazim…®n m…®tivasa zui.
\v 2 \x - \xo 24:2 \xt Jenesis 11:27\x*Egha Josua gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòIan ovaviba fom…®ra Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n ikia asebar ziaba fe. Men mav Tera, an Abraham ko Nahor…®n afeziam.
\v 3 \x - \xo 24:3 \xt Jenesis 12:1-9; 21:1-3\x*K…® ian ovavim Abraham, Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n a inigha iza Kenan…®n nguazim bar a garuigha, egha ovavir borir av…®riba a gan…®ga, Aisak sarama a gan…®ngi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 24:4 \xt Jenesis 25:24-26; 36:8; 46:1-7; God…®n Araziba 2:5\x*Egha otarir pumuning Aisak gan…®ngi, Jekop ko Iso. Egha Idom…®n danganim…®n m…®ghs…®aba itir nguazim isa Iso gan…®ngi, ez…® Jekop uan otariba ko, me Isip…®n kantrin iraghue.
\v 5 \x - \xo 24:5 \xt Ua Me Ini 3:1--12:42\x*Egha g…®n k…® ian inazir afeziaba bagha Moses ko Aron amadaz…®, aning Isipia bagha ghuz…®, k…® os…®mt…®zir ekiam Isipia ganigha bar me gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha g…®n ia inigha Isip…®n kantri ategha azenan ize.
\v 6 \x - \xo 24:6-7 \xt Ua Me Ini 14:1-31\x*K…® ian inazir afeziaba Isip…®n kantrin me inigha azenan izegha izima, Isipia hoziar karisba itiba inigha men ag…®ragha iza Ongarir Aghevim…®n oto.
\v 7 Ez…® ian inazir afeziaba atiatiava uarir akurvaghasa nan araima, k…® ghuariar p…®zim…®n me ko Isipia abigha tong…®rama anesara. Ez…® Israelia zuam…®ra ghua ongarim…®n vong…®n ghua nguazim…®n otoz…®, Isipia ongarir torim…®n men g…®n zuima, k…® ongarir otevimning gamiz…® aning iza ua uaning…®n suiragha, Isipia avaragha bar me kuavareme. Ia uari uan damazibar k…® Isipia gamizir bizir kam…®n ganigha fo. Ez…® g…®n ia bar dughiar ruarim…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ike.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 24:8 \xt D…®boboniba 21:21-35\x*‚Äú ‚ÄòEz…® k…® g…®n ia inigha aruem anadi nagh…®n, Amorian nguazir Jordan…®n Fanem…®n itim…®n ghuz…®, me ia ko m…®sozima k…® ian akuraz…®, ia me m…®sogha me ab…®ragha, men nguazim uari bagha a ini.
\v 9 \x - \xo 24:9-10 \xt D…®boboniba 22:1--24:25\x*Ez…® g…®n Sipor…®n otarim Balak, a Moapian atrivim, Israelia ia ko m…®soghasa. Egha a d…®kavigha, Beor…®n otarim Balam bagha akam amadagha ghaze, Balam akar kuratam ia m…®k…®m ia gas…®ghas…®ghasa.
\v 10 Ez…® Balam akar kuratam ia dan…®ngan k…® aghua. Egha k…® a gamiz…® a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibara a gan…®ngiz…®, k…® Balak…®n agharim…®n ua ia ini.
\v 11 \x - \xo 24:11 \xt Josua 3:14-17; 6:1-21\x*Ez…® g…®n ia Jordan…®n Fanem giregha ghua, Jerikon nguibam…®n otifi. Ez…® Jerikon m…®dorozir gumaziba ia m…®soghasava ami. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, Amoria, Peresia, Kenania, Hitia, Girgasia, Hivia, Jebusia, me bar uaghan ia ko m…®sozima, k…® ian akuraz…® ia me m…®sogha bar me ab…®ni.
\v 12 \x - \xo 24:12 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:28; God…®n Araziba 7:20\x*Dughiar kam, k…® ian faragha ghua ian apanibagh amiz…®, me bar atiatingi, ez…® bizir kam, Amorian atrivimning gamiz…®, aning arav ghu. Ia bizir kam uan m…®dorozir sababa ko barir pibar gavgavim…®n a gamizir puvat…®. K…®rara aning…®n ag…®raz…® aning arav ghu.
\v 13 \x - \xo 24:13 \xt God…®n Araziba 6:10-11\x*Ez…® nguazir k…® ia gan…®ngizir kam, ia a gis…®n ingangaritam at…®zir puvat…®, ez…® nguibar ekiar nguazir kam…®n aven itiba, ia uari tam…®n ingara anesarazir puvat…®gha, dat…®r…®gh…®n ia dar iti. Ia oparizir puvat…®zir oliv…®n temer ov…®ziba, ko wain…®n ov…®ziba, ia da oparizir puvat…®, ia pura da isava da api.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Egha Josua ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiating, an akabar g…®n mang…®va, guizbang…®ra an apengan ik…® an ingangarim damuva, uan inazir afeziabar aseba batokegh, kar me fom…®ra Mesopotemian kantri ko Isip…®n kantrin ikia dar ziaba fe.
\v 15 \x - \xo 24:15 \xt Rut 1:15; 1 Atriviba 18:21; Esekiel 20:39\x*Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fan aghuagh…®va derav…®ra n…®ghnigh, ia god…®n manam…®n ziam fam? Ian ovaviba fom…®ra Mesopotemian nguazim…®n ikia ziaba fezir aseba, ia da fam? O, Amoria, ia men nguazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n itir kam, men aseba, ia da fam? Ez…® k…® ko, nan d…®penim…®n itir adarazi bar mogh…®ra, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziamra fam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúE Ikiav…®ra Itir God ategh god…®n igharazibar ziaba fan kogham, bar puvat…®gham.
\v 17 E uan afeziaba ko, Isip…®n nguazim…®n ikia Isipia pura men apengan ikia, pura ingarir gumazir k…®nibar itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uab…® e inigha azenan ize. Ez…® e uari uan damazibar, an amizir mirakel…®n ekiar av…®ribar gani. Kantrin e aruibar aven, a bar derav…®rama e geghuvima, e zui.
\v 18 E zuir dughiam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God en faragha ghua, kantrin e mang…® otiv mangamiba, a bar me batuegha Amoria saram otoke. Amoria me faragha nguazir kam…®n ghuaviba. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a en God. Kamagh…®n e uaghan an ziam fasa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Josua me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa zuam…®ra kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, egh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, god…®n igharazitam a ko magh garir puvat…®. A uab…®ra, ia an ziam fasa a ifonge. Ia ak…®rim a gasaragh god…®n igharazibar ziaba f…®t…®, a ian arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan kogham.
\v 20 Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n deragha ia gami. Eght…® ia anetegh igharaz darazir asebar ziaba f…®t…®, a ian atar…®va pazav…®ra ia damigh, ivezir kuram ia danigh ia ag…®vagham.‚Äù
\v 21 Ez…® gumazamiziba Josua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®gham. E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziamra fam.‚Äù
\v 22 Ez…® Josua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari akam ak…®righa ghaze ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziamra fam.‚Äù Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar e amir kam, a guizbang…®ra.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Josua ua me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa ik…®zir igharazibar aser ian tong…®n itiba, da batokegh. Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, ia uan navir averiabar aven an ziamra f…®va, uari is…® a dan…®ngigh.‚Äù
\v 24 Ez…® gumazamiziba Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e an ziamra f…®va, an akam…®n g…®n mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Egha dughiar kam…®n me bar Sekem…®n nguibam…®n ikia, Josua gumazamizibar danganim inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir mam gami. Ez…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam, arazir God ifongeziba ko bizir God damuasa me m…®kemeziba, an aven iti. Eght…® gumazamiziba Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n g…®n mangam.
\v 26 Egha Josua akar kaba isava, God…®n Akar Gavgaviba itir Ak…®nafarim…®n aven da osiri. Egha dag…®ar ekiar mam inigha, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer danganim…®n borogh…®n temer Ok…®n povim…®n anesara.
\v 27 Egha Josua gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gan, e uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim g…®n…®ghn…®ghs…®, ia zurara dag…®ar asaraghav itir kam…®n gan. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, dag…®ar kam, bar ada baregha g…®fa. A kagh ababanim…®n m…®n ik…® n…®ghn…®zim ia dan…®ngt…®, ia uan God…®n akaba batoghan kogham.‚Äù
\v 28 Egha Josua gumazamiziba amadaz…® me uamategha uan nguibar me itibar ghue.
\s1 Josua ko Eleasar areme
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 24:29-31 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 2:7-9\x*Egha g…®n Nun…®n otarim Josua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim, a 110plan azeniba ikiava areme.
\v 30 \x - \xo 24:30 \xt Josua 19:49-50\x*Ez…® Israelia an kuam isa an nguazimra, Timnat Seran nguibam…®n anefa. Nguibar kam, Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n iti, a m…®ghs…®aba itir nguazim, egha not…®n amadaghan Gas…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n iti.
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® Josua ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fa ghua Josuan ovevem…®n g…®n, Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fav…®ra iti. Men gumazir dapaniba, bizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra Israelia bagha amizibar gani. Ez…® Israelian, gumazir dapanir kaba angam…®ra ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, me bar God…®n ziam fav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 32 \x - \xo 24:32 \xt Jenesis 33:19; 50:24-25; Ua Me Ini 13:19; Jon 4:5; Aposel 7:16\x*Bar fom…®ra, Israelian ovavim Jekop, Sekem…®n afeziam Hamor, an ovavir boriba da, nguazir otevir mam givese. An 100plan silvan dag…®abar nguazir kam givese. Bar g…®n Israelian gumazamiziba Isip…®n kantri ategha izir dughiam…®n, me uan inazir afeziam Josep…®n aghariba aterav…®ra iza bar abuan uan nguazim…®n ize. Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n Josep…®n aghariba isa, nguazir Jekop fom…®ra ivezezim…®n dar afa. Nguazir kam, a Josep…®n ovavir boribar nguazim.
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® Aron…®n otarim, Eleasar aremez…®, Israelia an kuam isa Gibean nguibam…®n anefa. Nguibar kam, an Efraim…®n anabam…®n m…®ghs…®aba itir nguazim…®n iti. Ez…® nguibar kam, an Eleasar…®n otarim Finias…®n nguibam.
